#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:14
msgid ""
"To activate the *Leads* setting, navigate to :menuselection:`CRM app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings` and check the box labeled, :guilabel:`Leads`. "
"Then, click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengaktifkan pengaturan *Lead*, kunjungi :menuselection:`Aplikasi CRM  "
"--> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan` dan centang kotak dengan "
"label, :guilabel:`Lead`. Lalu, klik :guilabel:`Simpan`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:None
msgid "Leads setting on CRM configuration page."
msgstr "Pengaturan lead pada halaman konfigurasi CRM."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:20
msgid ""
"Activating this feature adds the :guilabel:`Leads` menu option to the header "
"bar located along the top of the screen."
msgstr ""
"Mengaktifkan fitur ini menambahkan opsi menu :guilabel:`Leads` ke bilah "
"header yang terletak di sepanjang bagian atas layar."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:None
msgid "Leads menu on CRM application."
msgstr "Menu lead pada aplikasi CRM."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:26
msgid ""
"Once the *Leads* setting has been activated, it applies to all sales teams "
"by default. To turn off leads for a specific team, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`CRM app --> Configuration --> Sales Teams`. Then, select "
"a team from the list to open that team's configuration page. Clear "
"the :guilabel:`Leads` checkbox, located beneath the :guilabel:`Sales Team` "
"field, then click :icon:`fa-cloud-upload` :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah pengaturan *Leads* diaktifkan, berlaku untuk semua tim penjualan "
"secara default. Untuk mematikan leads untuk tim tertentu, buka "
":menuselection:`Aplikasi CRM --> Configuration --> Sales Teams`. Kemudian, "
"pilih tim dari daftar untuk membuka halaman konfigurasi tim tersebut. Hapus "
"centang pada checkbox :guilabel:`Leads`, yang terletak di bawah field "
":guilabel:`Sales Team`, kemudian klik :icon:`fa-cloud-upload` "
":guilabel:`Save`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:36
msgid "Convert a lead into an opportunity"
msgstr "Ubah prospek menjadi peluang"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:38
msgid ""
"To convert a lead into an *opportunity*, navigate to :menuselection:`CRM app "
"--> Leads`, and click on a lead from the list to open it."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengonversi lead menjadi *peluang*, kunjungi :menuselection:`Aplikasi "
"CRM --> Lead`, dan klik pada lead dari daftar untuk membukanya."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:42
msgid ""
"Attempting to convert a lead with a 100% probability into an opportunity "
"will result in an error message."
msgstr ""
"Mencoba mengonversi lead dengan probabilitas 100% menjadi peluang akan "
"menghasilkan pesan kesalahan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:0
msgid ""
"The error message that appears when attempting to convert a 100% probability "
"lead into\n"
"an opportunity."
msgstr ""
"Pesan kesalahan yang muncul saat mencoba mengonversi lead dengan "
"probabilitas 100% menjadi peluang."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:49
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Convert to Opportunity` button, located at the top-left "
"of the page."
msgstr ""
"Klik tombol :guilabel:`Konversi menjadi Peluang`, berlokasi di atas kiri "
"halaman."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:None
msgid "Create opportunity button on a lead record."
msgstr "Buat tombol peluang pada rekaman lead."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:54
msgid ""
"This opens a *Convert to opportunity* pop-up. Here, select "
"the :guilabel:`Convert to opportunity` option in the :guilabel:`Conversion "
"Action` field."
msgstr ""
"Ini membuka popup *Convert to opportunity*. Di sini, pilih opsi "
":guilabel:`Convert to opportunity` di field :guilabel:`Conversion Action`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:57
msgid ""
"Then, select a :guilabel:`Salesperson` and a :guilabel:`Sales Team` to which "
"the opportunity should be assigned. Neither field is required, but if a "
"selection is made in the :guilabel:`Salesperson` field, the :guilabel:`Sales "
"Team` is automatically populated based on the assignee's assigned team."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, pilih :guilabel:`Salesperson` dan :guilabel:`Sales Team` yang akan "
"ditugaskan peluang tersebut. Kedua field tidak wajib diisi, tetapi jika ada "
"pilihan yang dibuat di field :guilabel:`Salesperson`, :guilabel:`Sales Team` "
"akan otomatis terisi berdasarkan tim yang ditugaskan kepada assignee."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:61
msgid ""
"If the lead has already been assigned to a salesperson or a team, these "
"fields automatically populate with that information."
msgstr ""
"Bila lead sudah ditugaskan ke salesperson atau tim, field-field tersebut "
"otomatis diisi dengan informasi tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:64
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Customer` heading, choose from the following options:"
msgstr "Di bawah heading :guilabel:`Pelanggan`, pilih dari opsi-opsi berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:66
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Create a new customer`: Choose this option to use the information "
"in the lead to create a new customer record."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Create a new customer`: Pilih opsi ini untuk menggunakan "
"informasi dalam lead untuk membuat record pelanggan baru."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:68
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Link to an existing customer`: Choose this option, then select a "
"customer from the drop-down menu to link this opportunity to."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Link to an existing customer`: Pilih opsi ini, lalu pilih "
"pelanggan dari menu drop-down untuk menghubungkan peluang ini."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:71
msgid ""
"Lastly, when all configurations are complete, click :guilabel:`Create "
"Opportunity`."
msgstr ""
"Terakhir, saat semua konfigurasi selesai, klik :guilabel:`Buat Peluang`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:None
msgid "Create opportunity pop-up."
msgstr "Buat pop-up peluang."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:76
msgid ""
"To view the newly created opportunity, navigate to :menuselection:`CRM app --"
"> My Pipeline`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat peluang yang baru dibuat, kunjungi :menuselection:`Aplikasi "
"CRM -->  Pipeline Saya`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:79
#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/pipeline/merge_similar.rst:35
msgid "Merging similar leads and opportunities"
msgstr "Menggabungkan prospek dan peluang yang serupa"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:81
msgid ""
"If a :guilabel:`Similar Leads` smart button appears at the top of the page "
"for the lead, a similar lead or opportunity already exists in the database. "
"Before converting the current lead, click the smart button to check if the "
"leads should be merged."
msgstr ""
"Jika tombol pintar :guilabel:`Similar Leads` muncul di bagian atas halaman "
"untuk lead tersebut, lead atau peluang serupa sudah ada di database. Sebelum "
"mengonversi lead saat ini, klik tombol pintar untuk memeriksa apakah lead "
"harus digabungkan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:0
msgid "Close up of a lead with emphasis on the Similar Leads smart button."
msgstr "Tampilan dekat lead dengan penekanan pada tombol cerdas Lead Mirip."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:88
msgid ""
"To merge this lead with an existing similar lead or opportunity, click "
"the :guilabel:`Convert to Opportunity` button and select :guilabel:`Merge "
"with existing opportunities` in the :guilabel:`Conversion Action` field. "
"This generates a list of the similar leads/opportunities to be merged."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menggabungkan prospek ini dengan prospek atau peluang serupa yang "
"sudah ada, klik tombol :guilabel:`Konversi ke Peluang` dan pilih "
":guilabel:`Gabungkan dengan peluang yang ada` di kolom :guilabel:`Tindakan "
"Konversi`. Ini akan menghasilkan daftar prospek/peluang serupa yang akan "
"digabungkan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert.rst:93
msgid ""
"When merging, Odoo gives priority to whichever lead/opportunity was created "
"in the system first, merging the information into the first created lead/"
"opportunity. The resulting record is an opportunity."
msgstr ""
"Saat menggabungkan, Odoo memberikan prioritas pada prospek/peluang yang "
"dibuat terlebih dahulu di sistem, menggabungkan informasi ke dalam prospek/"
"peluang yang dibuat pertama. Catatan yang dihasilkan adalah peluang."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:3
msgid "Create leads (from email or manually)"
msgstr "Buat lead (dari email atau secara manual)"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:8
msgid ""
"Leads can be added to the *CRM* app from custom email aliases, and by "
"manually creating new records. This is in addition to the leads and "
"opportunities created in the app through the :doc:`website contact form "
"<opportunities_form>`."
msgstr ""
"Lead dapat ditambahkan ke aplikasi *CRM* dari alias email kustom, dan secara "
"manual membuat rekaman baru. Ini sebagai tambahan ke lead dan peluang yang "
"dibuat di aplikasi melalui :doc:`formulir kontak website "
"<opportunities_form>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:12
msgid ""
"First, ensure the *Leads* feature is enabled in the database by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`CRM app --> Configuration --> Settings`. Tick "
"the :guilabel:`Leads` checkbox, then click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Pertama, pastikan fitur *Lead* diaktifkan di database dengan "
"mengunjungi :menuselection:`Aplikasi CRM --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`. "
"Centang kotak :guilabel:`Lead`, lalu klik :guilabel:`Simpan`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:19
msgid "Configure email aliases"
msgstr "Konfigurasi alias email"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:21
msgid ""
"Each sales team has the option to create and utilize their own unique email "
"alias. When messages are sent to this address, a lead (or opportunity), is "
"created with the information from the message."
msgstr ""
"Setiap tim sales memiliki opsi untuk membuat dan menggunakan alias unik "
"untuk email mereka sendiri. Saat pesan dikirim ke alamat email ini, lead "
"(atau peluang), dibuat dengan informasi dari pesan tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:25
msgid ""
"To create or update a sales teams' email alias, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`CRM app --> Configuration --> Sales Teams`. Click on a "
"team from the list to open the team's details page."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat atau mengupdate alias email tim sales, "
"kunjungi :menuselection:`Aplikasi CRM --> Konfigurasi --> Tim Sales`. Klik "
"pada tim dari daftar untuk membuka halaman detail tim."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:None
msgid "The sales team details page, focused on the email alias section."
msgstr "Halaman detail tim sales, terpusat pada bagian alias email."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:32
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Email Alias` field, enter a name for the email alias, or "
"edit the existing name. In the :guilabel:`Accept Emails From` field, use the "
"drop-down menu to choose who is allowed to send messages to this email alias:"
msgstr ""
"Di field :guilabel:`Alias Email`, masukkan nama untuk alias email, atau edit "
"nama yang tersedia. Di field :guilabel:`Terima Email Dari`, gunakan menu "
"drop-down untuk memilih siapa yang diizinkan untuk mengirim pesan ke alias "
"email ini:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:36
msgid ":guilabel:`Everyone`: messages are accepted from any email address."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Semua Orang`: email diterima dari alamat email apa pun."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:37
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Authenticated Partners`: only accepts messages from email "
"addresses associated with a a partner (contact or customer) record."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Partner yang Diautentikasi`: hanya menerima pesan dari alamat "
"email terkait dengan rekaman partner (kontak atau pelanggan)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:39
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Followers only`: only accepts messages from those who are "
"following a record related to the team, such as a lead or opportunity. "
"Messages are also accepted from team members."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Hanya pengikut`: hanya menerima pesan dari mereka yang mengikuti "
"rekaman terkait tim, seperti lead atau peluang. Pesan juga diterima dari "
"anggota tim."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:41
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Authenticated Employees`: only accepts messages from email "
"addresses that are connected to a record in the *Employees* app."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Karyawan yang Diautentikasi`: hanya menerima pesan dari alamat "
"email yang terhubung ke rekaman di aplikasi *Karyawan*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:45
msgid "Leads created from email"
msgstr "Lead dibuat dari email"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:47
msgid ""
"Leads created from email alias messages can be viewed by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`CRM app --> Leads`. Click a lead from the list to open "
"it, and view the details."
msgstr ""
"Lead dibuat dari pesan alias email dapat dilihat dengan "
"mengunjungi :menuselection:`Aplikasi CRM --> Lead`. Klik lead dari daftar "
"untuk membukanya, dan lihat detail."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:50
msgid ""
"The email received by the alias is added to the *chatter* thread for the "
"lead. The subject line of the message is added to the title field, and "
"the :guilabel:`Email` field is updated with the contact's email address."
msgstr ""
"Email diterima melalui alias ditambahkan ke thread *obrolan* untuk lead. "
"Baris subject pesan ditambahkan ke field judul, dan field :guilabel:`Email` "
"diupdate dengan alamat email kontak."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:None
msgid "The chatter thread of a newly created lead in the CRM app."
msgstr "Thread obrolan dari lead yang baru dibuat di aplikasi CRM."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:59
msgid ""
"If the *leads* feature is **not** enabled on the database, messages to the "
"email alias are added to the database as opportunities."
msgstr ""
"Bila fitur *lead* **tidak** diaktifkan di database, pesan ke alias email "
"ditambahkan ke database sebagai peluang."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:63
msgid ":doc:`../../../general/email_communication`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../../general/email_communication`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:66
msgid "Manually create leads"
msgstr "Secara manual buat lead"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:68
msgid ""
"Leads can be added directly to the *CRM* app by manually creating a new "
"record. Navigate to :menuselection:`CRM app --> Leads` to view a list of "
"existing leads."
msgstr ""
"Lead dapat ditambahkan langsung ke aplikasi *CRM& dengan secara manual "
"membuat rekaman baru. Kunjungi :menuselection:`Aplikasi CRM --> Lead` untuk "
"melihat daftar lead yang sudah tersedia."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:72
msgid ""
"Leads can also be added via the :doc:`Generate Leads <lead_mining>` button."
msgstr ""
"Lead juga dapat ditambahkan melalui tombol :doc:`Buat Lead <lead_mining>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:74
msgid ""
"At the top-left of the list, click :guilabel:`New` to open a "
"blank :guilabel:`Leads` form."
msgstr ""
"Di atas kiri daftar, klik :guilabel:`Baru` untuk membuka "
"formulir :guilabel:`Lead` kosong."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:76
msgid ""
"In the first field of the new form, enter a title for the new lead. Next, "
"enter a :guilabel:`Contact Name`, and a :guilabel:`Company Name`."
msgstr ""
"Di field pertama formulir baru, masukkan judul untuk lead baru. Setelah itu, "
"masukkan :guilabel:`Nama Kontak`, dan :guilabel:`Nama Perusahaan`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:80
msgid ""
"If a lead is :doc:`converted to an opportunity <convert>`, "
"the :guilabel:`Company Name` field is used to either link this opportunity "
"to an existing customer, or to create a new customer."
msgstr ""
"Bila lead :doc:`dikonversi menjadi peluang <convert>`, field :guilabel:`Nama "
"Perusahaan` digunakan untuk menghubungkan peluang ini ke pelanggan yang "
"tersedia, atau membuat pelanggan baru."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:84
msgid "Manually create opportunities"
msgstr "Secara manual membuat peluang"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:86
msgid ""
"To manually create an opportunity, navigate to :menuselection:`CRM app --> "
"Sales --> My Pipeline`. At the top-left of the page, click :guilabel:`New` "
"to create a new opportunity Kanban card. In the :guilabel:`Organization/"
"Contact` field, enter the name of the company the opportunity is for."
msgstr ""
"Untuk secara manual membuat peluang, kunjungi :menuselection:`Aplikasi CRM --"
"> Sales --> Pipeline Saya`. Di atas-kiri halaman, klik :guilabel:`Baru` "
"untuk membuat kartu Kanban peluang baru. Di field :guilabel:`Organisasi/"
"Kontak`, masukkan nama perusahaan untuk peluang."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:90
msgid ""
"Choose a name, and enter it in the :guilabel:`Opportunity` field. *This is a "
"required field.* When manually creating an opportunity, it is helpful to add "
"a name that relates to the details of the opportunity."
msgstr ""
"Pilih nama, dan masukkan ke field :guilabel:`Peluang`. *Ini adalah field "
"yang diperlukan.* Saat secara manual membuat peluang, akan membantu untuk "
"menambahkan nama yang terkait ke detail peluang."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:95
msgid ""
"In the example below, the opportunity is named `5 VP Chairs`. This "
"identifies the product the customer is interested in, as well as the "
"potential number of products."
msgstr ""
"Di contoh di bawah, peluang dinamakan `5 VP Chairs`. Ini mengidentifikasi "
"produk yang pelanggan minati, sekaligus kemungkinan jumlah produk."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:0
msgid "An example of an opportunity in the CRM pipeline."
msgstr "Contoh peluang di pipeline CRM."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:102
msgid ""
"Enter the contact information for the opportunity in the :guilabel:`Email` "
"and :guilabel:`Phone` fields."
msgstr ""
"Masukkan informasi kontak untuk peluang di field :guilabel:`Email` "
"dan :guilabel:`Telepon`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:105
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Expected Revenue` field, enter an estimated value for the "
"opportunity."
msgstr ""
"Di field :guilabel:`Pendapatan yang Diharapkan`, masukkan estimasi nilai "
"peluang."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:108
msgid ""
"The information in the :guilabel:`Expected Revenue` and priority fields can "
"be used to track performance for individual salespeople, and on a team "
"basis. See :doc:`../performance/expected_revenue_report` and :doc:`../"
"track_leads/lead_scoring` for more information."
msgstr ""
"Informasi di :guilabel:`Pendapatan yang Diharapkan` dan field prioritas "
"dapat digunakan untuk melacak performa untuk setiap salesperson secara "
"individu dan secara tim. :doc:`../performance/expected_revenue_report` "
"dan :doc:`../track_leads/lead_scoring` untuk informasi lebih lanjut."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:113
msgid "Then, use the |st-o| :guilabel:`(star)` icons to assign a priority."
msgstr ""
"Lalu, gunakan ikon |st-o| :guilabel:`(star)` untuk memberikan prioritas."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:115
msgid "|st-o| |st-o| |st-o|: low priority"
msgstr "|st-o| |st-o| |st-o|: prioritas rendah"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:116
msgid "|st| |st-o| |st-o|: medium priority"
msgstr "|st| |st-o| |st-o|: prioritas menengah"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:117
msgid "|st| |st| |st-o|: high priority"
msgstr "|st| |st| |st-o|: prioritas tinggi"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:118
msgid "|st| |st| |st|: very high priority"
msgstr "|st| |st| |st|: prioritas sangat tinggi"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:121
msgid ""
"Assigning a priority changes the order of leads in Kanban view, with higher "
"priority leads displayed first."
msgstr ""
"Menugaskan prioritas mengubah urutan lead di tampilan Kanban, dengan "
"prioritas lebih tinggi ditampilkan terlebih dahulu."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:124
msgid ""
"Once all the necessary information has been entered, click :guilabel:`Add`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah semua informasi yanag diperlukan telah dimasukkan, "
"klik :guilabel:`Tambah`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/email_manual.rst:None
msgid "The CRM pipeline with a newly created opportunity."
msgstr "Pipeline CRM dengan peluang yang baru dibuat."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:3
msgid "Lead mining"
msgstr "Lead mining"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:8
msgid ""
"*Lead mining* is a feature that allows *CRM* users to generate new leads "
"directly within their Odoo database. To ensure lead qualification, lead "
"mining output is determined by a variety of filtering criteria, such as the "
"country, the company size, and the industry."
msgstr ""
"*Lead mining* adalah fitur yang memungkinkan pengguna *CRM* untuk "
"menghasilkan prospek baru langsung di dalam database Odoo mereka. Untuk "
"memastikan kualifikasi prospek, output lead mining ditentukan oleh berbagai "
"kriteria penyaringan, seperti negara, ukuran perusahaan, dan industri."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:15
msgid ""
"To get started, go to :menuselection:`CRM app --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`, and select the :guilabel:`Lead Mining` checkbox to activate the "
"feature. Then, click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memulai, buka :menuselection:`Aplikasi CRM --> Konfigurasi --> "
"Pengaturan`, dan pilih kotak centang :guilabel:`Lead Mining` untuk "
"mengaktifkan fitur tersebut. Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Simpan`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:None
msgid "Activate lead mining in Odoo CRM settings."
msgstr "Aktifkan lead mining di pengaturan Odoo CRM."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:22
msgid "Generate leads"
msgstr "Buat lead"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:25
msgid ""
"If the :doc:`Leads </applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert>` feature "
"is not enabled, then lead generation creates opportunities instead."
msgstr ""
"Jika fitur :doc:`Prospek </applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/convert>` "
"tidak diaktifkan, maka pembuatan prospek akan membuat peluang sebagai "
"gantinya."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:28
msgid ""
"With the *Lead Mining* setting activated, the *Generate Leads* button is "
"added to the upper-left corner of the *CRM* *Pipeline* (:menuselection:`CRM "
"app --> Sales --> My Pipeline`). Lead mining requests are also available "
"through :menuselection:`CRM app --> Configuration --> Lead Mining Requests` "
"and through :menuselection:`CRM app --> Leads`, where "
"the :guilabel:`Generate Leads` button is also available."
msgstr ""
"Dengan pengaturan *Lead Mining* diaktifkan, tombol *Generate Leads* "
"ditambahkan ke sudut kiri atas *Pipeline* *CRM* (:menuselection:`Aplikasi "
"CRM --> Penjualan --> Pipeline Saya`). Permintaan lead mining juga tersedia "
"melalui :menuselection:`Aplikasi CRM --> Konfigurasi --> Permintaan Lead "
"Mining` dan melalui :menuselection:`Aplikasi CRM --> Prospek`, di mana "
"tombol :guilabel:`Generate Leads` juga tersedia."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:34
msgid ""
"From any of these locations, click the :guilabel:`Generate Leads` button, "
"and a pop-up window appears."
msgstr ""
"Dari salah satu lokasi ini, klik tombol :guilabel:`Generate Leads`, dan "
"jendela pop-up akan muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:None
msgid ""
"The pop-up window with the selection criteria in order to generate leads in "
"Odoo."
msgstr "Jendela pop-up dengan kriteria pilihan untuk membuat lead di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:40
msgid ""
"Leads can be generated for :guilabel:`Companies` to get company information "
"only, or for |CC| to get both company information and contact information "
"for individual employees."
msgstr ""
"Prospek dapat dihasilkan untuk :guilabel:`Perusahaan` untuk mendapatkan "
"informasi perusahaan saja, atau untuk |CC| untuk mendapatkan informasi "
"perusahaan dan informasi kontak untuk karyawan individu."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:43
msgid "Filtering options for generating leads include the following:"
msgstr "Opsi penyaringan untuk menghasilkan prospek meliputi:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:45
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Countries`: Filter leads based on the country (or countries) they "
"are located in."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Negara`: Filter prospek berdasarkan negara (atau negara-negara) "
"tempat mereka berada."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:46
msgid ""
":guilabel:`States`: Filter leads even further based on the state in which "
"they are located, if applicable."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Provinsi`: Filter prospek lebih lanjut berdasarkan provinsi "
"tempat mereka berada, jika berlaku."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:48
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Industries`: Filter leads based on the specific industry they "
"work in."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Industri`: Filter prospek berdasarkan industri spesifik tempat "
"mereka bekerja."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:49
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Filter on Size`: Generates a field labeled :guilabel:`Size`. Fill "
"in the blanks to create a range for the desired company size based on its "
"number of employees."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Filter berdasarkan Ukuran`: Menghasilkan bidang berlabel "
":guilabel:`Ukuran`. Isi bagian kosong untuk membuat rentang ukuran "
"perusahaan yang diinginkan berdasarkan jumlah karyawannya."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:53
msgid ""
"When using |CC|, generated contacts can also be filtered based on "
"their :guilabel:`Role` or :guilabel:`Seniority`."
msgstr ""
"Saat menggunakan |CC|, kontak yang dihasilkan juga dapat difilter "
"berdasarkan :guilabel:`Peran` atau :guilabel:`Senioritas` mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:56
msgid ""
"Additionally, there are options for sales team assignment and internal "
"tracking:"
msgstr ""
"Selain itu, terdapat opsi untuk penugasan tim penjualan dan pelacakan "
"internal:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:58
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Sales Team`: Set which Sales Team the leads will be assigned to."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tim Penjualan`: Tetapkan Tim Penjualan mana yang akan ditugaskan "
"prospek."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:59
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Salesperson`: Set which member of the Sales Team the leads will "
"be assigned to."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tenaga Penjualan`: Tetapkan anggota Tim Penjualan mana yang akan "
"ditugaskan prospek."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:60
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Default Tags`: Set which tags are applied directly to the leads "
"once found."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tag Default`: Tetapkan tag mana yang langsung diterapkan ke "
"prospek setelah ditemukan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:63
msgid ""
"If applicable, make sure to be aware of the latest EU regulations when "
"receiving contact information. Learn more about the General Data Protection "
"Regulation on `Odoo GDPR <http://odoo.com/gdpr>`_."
msgstr ""
"Jika berlaku, pastikan untuk mengetahui peraturan UE terbaru saat menerima "
"informasi kontak. Pelajari lebih lanjut tentang General Data Protection "
"Regulation di `Odoo GDPR <http://odoo.com/gdpr>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:68
msgid "View leads"
msgstr "Lihat lead"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:70
msgid ""
"After leads are generated, they are assigned to the designated salesperson "
"and team. To view additional information regarding the lead, select one from "
"the list and click to open it."
msgstr ""
"Setelah prospek dibuat, prospek tersebut ditugaskan kepada tenaga penjualan "
"dan tim yang ditunjuk. Untuk melihat informasi tambahan mengenai prospek, "
"pilih salah satu dari daftar dan klik untuk membukanya."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:73
msgid ""
"Additional information for the lead is provided in its chatter. This can "
"include the number of employees that work for the lead, the technology it "
"uses, its timezone, and any direct contact information."
msgstr ""
"Informasi tambahan untuk prospek disediakan dalam chatter-nya. Ini dapat "
"mencakup jumlah karyawan yang bekerja untuk prospek tersebut, teknologi yang "
"digunakannya, zona waktunya, dan informasi kontak langsung apa pun."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:None
msgid "The chatter thread of a newly generated lead."
msgstr "Thread obrolan lead yang baru dibuat"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:81
#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/lead_enrichment.rst:80
#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/partner_autocomplete.rst:47
#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental.rst:68
msgid "Pricing"
msgstr "Harga"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:83
msgid ""
"Lead mining is an *In-App Purchase* service, and each generated lead costs "
"one :ref:`credit <in_app_purchase/credits>`. When using the |CC| option to "
"generate leads, one additional credit is used for each contact generated. "
"See here for complete pricing information: `Lead Generation by Odoo IAP "
"<https://iap.odoo.com/iap/in-app-services/167?>`_. Enterprise Odoo users "
"with a valid subscription get free credits to test |IAP| features before "
"purchasing more credits for the database. This includes demo/training "
"databases, educational databases, and one-app-free databases."
msgstr ""
"Lead mining adalah layanan *In-App Purchase*, dan setiap prospek yang "
"dihasilkan memerlukan satu :ref:`kredit <in_app_purchase/credits>`. Saat "
"menggunakan opsi |CC| untuk menghasilkan prospek, satu kredit tambahan "
"digunakan untuk setiap kontak yang dihasilkan. Lihat di sini untuk informasi "
"harga lengkap: `Lead Generation by Odoo IAP <https://iap.odoo.com/iap/in-app-"
"services/167?>`_. Pengguna Odoo Enterprise dengan langganan yang valid "
"mendapatkan kredit gratis untuk menguji fitur |IAP| sebelum membeli lebih "
"banyak kredit untuk database. Ini termasuk database demo/pelatihan, database "
"pendidikan, dan database satu-aplikasi-gratis."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:90
msgid ""
"To buy credits, navigate to :menuselection:`CRM app --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`. In the :guilabel:`Lead Generation` section, under "
"the :guilabel:`Lead Mining` feature, click :guilabel:`Manage Service & Buy "
"Credits` to go to the Lead Generation Settings page. Click :guilabel:`Buy "
"Credit` to go to the *Odoo IAP* page where you'll be able to buy packs of "
"Lead Generation credits."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membeli kredit, buka :menuselection:`Aplikasi CRM --> Konfigurasi --> "
"Pengaturan`. Di bagian :guilabel:`Lead Generation`, di bawah fitur "
":guilabel:`Lead Mining`, klik :guilabel:`Kelola Layanan & Beli Kredit` untuk "
"membuka halaman Pengaturan Lead Generation. Klik :guilabel:`Beli Kredit` "
"untuk membuka halaman *Odoo IAP* di mana Anda dapat membeli paket kredit "
"Lead Generation."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:96
msgid ""
"Credits may also be purchased by navigating directly to the `Odoo IAP "
"<https://iap.odoo.com/>`_ page and clicking the :guilabel:`Lead Generation` "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Kredit juga dapat dibeli dengan langsung membuka halaman `Odoo IAP <https://"
"iap.odoo.com/>`_ dan mengklik tombol :guilabel:`Lead Generation`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/lead_enrichment.rst:None
msgid "Buy credits in the Odoo IAP settings."
msgstr "Beli kredit di pengaturan Odoo IAP."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:103
msgid ""
"Credits are **not** interchangeable between IAP services. *Lead Generation* "
"credits may not be spent on other IAP services, and no other IAP credits can "
"be spent on *Lead Generation*."
msgstr ""
"Kredit **tidak** dapat ditukar antar layanan IAP. Kredit *Lead Generation* "
"tidak dapat digunakan untuk layanan IAP lainnya, dan tidak ada kredit IAP "
"lain yang dapat digunakan untuk *Lead Generation*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:107
msgid ":doc:`/applications/essentials/in_app_purchase`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/essentials/in_app_purchase`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:3
msgid "Create opportunities from web contact forms"
msgstr "Buat peluang dari formulir kontak website"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:5
msgid ""
"Adding a contact form to a website makes it easy to convert visitors into "
"leads and opportunities. After a visitor submits their information, an "
"opportunity can be created automatically, and assigned to a designated sales "
"team and salesperson."
msgstr ""
"Menambahkan formulir kontak ke website membuat konversi pengunjung menjadi "
"lead dan peluang lebih mudah. Setelah pengunjung menyerahkan informasi "
"mereka, peluang dapat dibuat otomatis, dan ditugaskan ke tim sales dan "
"salesperson terpilih."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:12
msgid "Customize contact forms"
msgstr "Kustomisasi formulir kontak"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:14
msgid ""
"By default, the *Contact Us* page on an Odoo website displays a "
"preconfigured contact form. This form can be customized, as needed, to suit "
"the needs of a specific sales team."
msgstr ""
"Secara default, halaman *Hubungi Kami* di website Odoo menampilkan formulir "
"kontak yang sudah dikonfigurasi. Formulir ini dapat dikustomisasi, sesuai "
"kebutuhan, untuk memenuhi kebutuhan tim sales tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:17
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Website app --> Contact Us`, then "
"click :guilabel:`Edit` in the top-right of the screen to open the web "
"editor. Click on the form building block in the body of the webpage to open "
"the form configuration settings on the right sidebar. The following options "
"are available to customize the contact form from the :guilabel:`From` "
"section of the right sidebar:"
msgstr ""
"Kunjungi :menuselection:`Applikasi website --> Hubungi Kami`, lalu "
"klik :guilabel:`Edit` di atas-kanan layar untuk membuka editor website. Klik "
"formulir building block di bagian badan webpage untuk membuka pengaturan "
"konfigurasi formulir di kolom samping kanan. Opsi-opsi berikut tersedia "
"untuk mengustomisasi formulir kontak dari bagian :guilabel:`Formulir` di "
"kolom samping kanan:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:None
msgid "The form configuration settings on an Odoo website."
msgstr "Pengaturan konfigurasi formulir di website Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:26
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Action`: the default action for a contact form is :guilabel:`Send "
"an Email`. Select :guilabel:`Create an Opportunity` from the drop-down list "
"to capture the information in the *CRM* app."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Action`: tindakan default untuk formulir kontak "
"adalah :guilabel:`Kirim Email`. Pilih :guilabel:`Buat Peluang` dari daftar "
"drop-down untuk mengambil informasi di aplikasi *CRM*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:29
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Sales Team`: choose a sales team from the drop-down menu that the "
"opportunities from this form should be assigned to. This field **only** "
"appears if the :guilabel:`Action` field is set to :guilabel:`Create an "
"Opportunity`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tim Sales`: pilih tim sales dari menu drop-down yang akan "
"ditugaskan peluang dari formulir ini. Field ini **hanya** muncul bila "
"field :guilabel:`Action` ditetapkan untuk :guilabel:`Membuat Peluang`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:32
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Salesperson`: if the opportunities should be assigned to a "
"specific salesperson, select them from the drop-down menu. If no selection "
"is made in this field, the opportunities are assigned based on the team's "
"existing rules."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Salesperson`: bila peluang akan ditugaskan ke salesperson "
"tertentu, pilih mereka dari menu drop-down. Bila tidak ada pilihan yang "
"dibuat di field ini, peluang akan ditugaskan berrdasarkan peraturan tim yang "
"tersedia."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:35
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Marked Fields`: use this field to alter how the form handles "
"marked fields. The default option is to treat marked fields "
"as :guilabel:`Required`, which is the recommended setting."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Field Bertanda`: gunakan field ini untuk mengubah bagaimana "
"formulir menangani field-field bertanda. Opsi standar adalah untuk "
"memperlakukan field bertanda sebagai :guilabel:`Diperlukan`, yang merupakan "
"pengaturan yang direkomendasikan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:37
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Mark Text`: choose how :guilabel:`Marked Fields` should be "
"identified. The default character is an asterisk (`*`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tandai Teks`: pilih bagaimana :guilabel:`Field Bertanda` akan "
"diidentifikasi. Karakter default adalah asterisk (`*`)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:39
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Labels Width`: use this field to alter the pixel width of the "
"labels, if desired."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Lebar Label`: gunakan field ini untuk mengubah lebar pixel label, "
"bila diinginkan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:40
msgid ""
":guilabel:`On Success`: select how the webpage reacts after a customer "
"successfully submits a form. :guilabel:`Nothing` keeps the customer on the "
"same screen, with the addition of a confirmation message that the form was "
"submitted successfully. :guilabel:`Redirect` sends the customer to a new "
"webpage, based on the address provided in the :guilabel:`URL` field "
"below. :guilabel:`Show Message` replaces the form with a preconfigured "
"message that informs the customer someone should respond to them as soon as "
"possible."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Saat Sukses`: pilih bagaimana webpage bereaksi setelah pelanggan "
"sukses menyerahkan formulir :guilabel:`Tidak Ada` tetap membiarkan pelanggan "
"di layar yang sama, dengan tambahan pesan konfirmasi bahwa formulir telah "
"sukses diserahkan. :guilabel:`Alihkan Ulang` mengirim pelanggan ke webpage "
"baru, berdasarkan alamat yang disediakan di field :guilabel:`URL` di "
"bawah. :guilabel:`Tunjukkan Pesan` mengganti formulir dengan pesan yang "
"dikonfigurasi sebelumnya yang menginformasikan pelanggan bahwa akan ada "
"seseorang yang menghubungi mereka secepat mungkin."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:46
msgid ""
":guilabel:`URL`: if :guilabel:`Redirect` is selected in the :guilabel:`On "
"Success` field, enter the URL for the webpage, where customers should be "
"directed after successfully submitting a form."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`URL`: bila :guilabel:`Alihkan Ulang` dipilih di "
"field :guilabel:`Saat Sukses`, masukkan URL untuk webpage, yang akan "
"pelanggan kunjungi setelah sukses menyerahkan formulir"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:48
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Visibility`: use the drop-down menu to add any visibility "
"conditions for this field, if desired."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Visibilitas`: gunakan menu drop-down untuk menambahkan kondisi "
"visibilitas apa pun untuk field ini, bila diinginkan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:52
msgid ""
"If *leads* are activated in *CRM* settings, selecting :guilabel:`Create an "
"Opportunity` generates a lead instead. To activate leads, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`CRM app --> Configuration --> Settings`, and tick "
"the :guilabel:`Leads` checkbox. Then, click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Bila *lead* diaktifkan di pengaturan *CRM*, memilih :guilabel:`Buat Peluang` "
"akan membuat lead. Untuk mengaktifkan lead, "
"kunjungi :menuselection:`Aplikasi CRM --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`, dan "
"centang kotak :guilabel:`Lead`. Lalu, klik :guilabel:`Simpan`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:57
msgid "Customize contact form fields"
msgstr "Kustomisasikan field formulir kontak"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:59
msgid ""
"In addition to the settings for the form, the settings for each field can be "
"customized, as well. With the web editor menu still open, click into a field "
"to open the :guilabel:`Field` configuration settings section on the sidebar. "
"The following options are available to customize a field:"
msgstr ""
"Ditambah pengaturan untuk formulir, pengaturan untuk setiap field dapat "
"dikustomisasi juga. Dengan menu editor website yang masih terbuka, klik ke "
"field untuk membuka bagian pengaturan konfigurasi :guilabel:`Field` di kolom "
"samping. Opsi-opsi berikut tersedia untuk mengustomisasi field:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:63
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Type`: choose a custom field option or an existing field type."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tipe`: pilih opsi field kustom atau tipe field yang terdedia."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:64
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Input Type`: determine the type of information customers should "
"input. Available options "
"are :guilabel:`Text`, :guilabel:`Email`, :guilabel:`Telephone`, "
"or :guilabel:`Url`. The selection made in this field limits the format that "
"customers can use when entering information."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tipe Input`: menentukan tipe informasi yang pelanggan harus "
"masukkan. Opsi yang tersedia "
"adalah :guilabel:`Teks`, :guilabel:`Email`, :guilabel:`Telepon`, "
"atau :guilabel:`Url`. Pilihan yang dibuat di field membatasi format yang "
"pelanggan dapat gunakan saat memasukkan informasi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:67
msgid ":guilabel:`Label`: enter the name for the field."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Label`: memasukkan nama untuk field."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:68
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Position`: choose the way the label is aligned with the rest of "
"the form. The label can be hidden, above the field, to the left of the "
"field, or right adjusted and closer to the field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Posisi`: pilih cara label akan diselaraskan dengan sisa formulir. "
"Label dapat disembunyikan, di atas field, di kiri field, atau disesuaikan di "
"kanan dan lebih dekat ke field."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:70
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Description`: slide the toggle to add a description for the "
"field, which can provide additional instructions to customers. Click under "
"the field on the form to add the description."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Deskripsi`: geser toggle untuk menambahkan deskripsi untuk field, "
"yang akan menyediakan insturksi tambahan ke pelanggan. Klik di bawah field "
"di formulir untuk menambahkan deskripsi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:72
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Placeholder`: enter an example to help users know how to input "
"information where formatting is important, such as a phone number or email "
"address."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Placeholder`: masukkan contoh untuk membantu user mengetahui "
"bagaimana cara memasukkan informasi di mana formatting itu penting, seperti "
"nomor telepon atau alamat email."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:74
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Default Value`: enter a value to include in the form, by default, "
"if the customer does not provide information in the field. *It is not "
"recommended to include a default value for required fields*."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Default Value`: masukkan value untuk diikutsertakan di formulir "
"secara standar, bila pelanggan tidak menyediakan informasi di field. *Tidak "
"direkomendasikan untuk memasukkan default value untuk field yang diperlukan*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:77
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Required`: slide the toggle to mark this field as required if it "
"**must** be filled in for every submission."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Diperlukan`: geser toggle untuk menandai field ini sebagai "
"diperlukan bila **harus** diisi di setiap penyerahan formulir."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:79
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Visibility`: select when this field should be visible. Use the "
"button on the left to choose whether to show or hide this field on a desktop "
"users. Use the button on the right to choose whether to show or hide this "
"field to mobile users."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Visibilitas`: pilih kapan field ini harus terlihat. Gunakan "
"tombol di kiri untuk memilih apakah untuk menunjukkan atau menyembunyikkan "
"field ini untuk user desktop. Gunakan tombol di kanan untuk memilih apakah "
"untuk menunjukkan field ini untuk user mobile."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:82
msgid ":guilabel:`Animation`: select if this field should have any animation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Animasi`: pilih bila field ini harus memiliki animasi apa pun."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:None
msgid "The field configuration settings on an Odoo website."
msgstr "Pengaturan konfigurasi field di website Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:89
msgid "View opportunities"
msgstr "Lihat peluang"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:91
msgid ""
"After a customer submits a contact form, and an opportunity is created, it "
"is assigned based on the :ref:`form settings <crm/customize-contact-form>`. "
"To view opportunities, navigate to :menuselection:`CRM app --> Sales --> My "
"Pipeline`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah pelanggan menyerahkan formulir kontak, dan peluang dibuat, akan "
"ditugaskan berdasarkan :ref:`pengaturan formulir <crm/customize-contact-"
"form>`. Untuk melihat peluang, kunjungi :menuselection:`Aplikasi CRM --> "
"Sales --> Pipeline Saya`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:96
msgid ""
"If leads are activated on the database, contact form submissions are "
"generated as leads, not opportunities. To activate leads, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`CRM app --> Configuration --> Settings`, and tick "
"the :guilabel:`Leads` checkbox. Then, click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Bila lead diaktifkan di database, penyerahan formulir kontak dibuat sebagai "
"lead, bukan peluang. Untuk mengaktifkan lead, "
"kunjungi :menuselection:`Aplikasi CRM --> Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`, dan "
"centang kotak :guilabel:`Lead`. Lalu, klik :guilabel:`Simpan`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:100
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`CRM app --> Leads` to view the newly-created "
"leads."
msgstr ""
"Kunjungi :menuselection:`Aplikasi CRM --> Lead` untuk melihat lead yang baru "
"saja dibuat."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:102
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`My Pipeline` dashboard, click on an opportunity card in "
"the Kanban view to open the opportunity record. The information submitted by "
"the customer is visible on the opportunity record."
msgstr ""
"Di :guilabel:`Pipeline Saya` dashboard, klik pada kartu peluang di tampilan "
"Kanban untuk membuka rekaman peluang. Informasi yang diserahkan oleh "
"pelanggan terlihat di rekaman peluang."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:107
msgid ""
"As the contact form fields are customizable, the fields on the opportunity "
"record, where the form information is stored, varies accordingly."
msgstr ""
"Karena field formulir kontak dapat dikustomisasi, field di rekaman peluang, "
"di mana informasi formulir disimpan, akan berbeda-beda."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:110
msgid ""
"If the preconfigured contact form is used, the *Subject* field is added to "
"the :guilabel:`Title` field, and the content in the :guilabel:`Notes` field, "
"which is labeled as :guilabel:`Your Question`, is added to "
"the :guilabel:`Internal Notes` tab."
msgstr ""
"Bila formulir kontak yang dikonfigurasi sebelumnya digunakan, field "
"*Subject* ditambahkan ke field :guilabel:`Judul`, dan konten di "
"field :guilabel:`Catatan`, yang dilabel sebagai :guilabel:`Pertanyaan Anda`, "
"ditambahkan ke tab :guilabel:`Catatan Internal`."

