#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/self_order.rst:68
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Home buttons` are displayed on the kiosk or mobile device "
"interfaces when customers are self-ordering. To set them up, click :icon:`fa-"
"arrow-right` :guilabel:`Home buttons`. Then,"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tombol Beranda` ditampilkan pada antarmuka kios atau perangkat "
