msgstr ":doc:`../../payment_methods`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:3
msgid "Glory"
msgstr "Glory"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:5
msgid ""
"**Glory** :doc:`cash machines <../cash_machines>` enable the automation of "
"cash transactions."
msgstr ""
"Mesin uang tunai **Glory** :doc:`cash machines <../cash_machines>` "
"memungkinkan otomatisasi transaksi uang tunai."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:8
msgid "Odoo supports the Glory CI-5, CI-10, and CI-10X models."
msgstr "Odoo mendukung model Glory CI-5, CI-10, dan CI-10X."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:9
msgid ""
"The Glory machine must run firmware version ISP-K05H/B v18.40 or later. Any "
"version starting with ISP-K35 is **not supported**."
msgstr ""
"Mesin Glory harus menjalankan firmware versi ISP-K05H/B v18.40 atau yang "
"lebih baru. Versi apa pun yang dimulai dengan ISP-K35 **tidak didukung**."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:12
msgid ""
"The integration with the Glory cash machine only supports basic functions, "
"such as cash transactions and cash count checks."
msgstr ""
"Integrasi dengan mesin uang tunai Glory hanya mendukung fungsi dasar, "
"seperti transaksi uang tunai dan pemeriksaan jumlah uang tunai."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:23
msgid "Cash machine settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan mesin uang tunai"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:25
msgid ""
"Power on the cash machine, which briefly displays its IP address at the "
"bottom of the screen. Note it down for later."
msgstr ""
"Nyalakan mesin uang tunai, yang akan menampilkan alamat IP-nya secara "
"singkat di bagian bawah layar. Catat untuk digunakan nanti."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:29
msgid ""
"The IP address should be formatted as `###.###.#.##` (e.g., `192.168.0.25`)."
msgstr ""
"Alamat IP harus diformat sebagai `###.###.#.##` (misalnya, `192.168.0.25`)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:31
msgid ""
"Navigate to the cash machine's homepage by entering its IP address as the "
"URL in `HTTPS` (e.g., `https://192.168.0.25`), and log in with your Glory "
"credentials."
msgstr ""
"Navigasikan ke beranda mesin uang tunai dengan memasukkan alamat IP-nya "
"sebagai URL dalam `HTTPS` (misalnya, `https://192.168.0.25`), dan masuk "
"dengan kredensial Glory Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:33
msgid ""
"As long as the certificate is not imported, a warning page appears when "
"trying to access the machine's homepage. Bypass it by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Advanced` and then :guilabel:`Proceed to [IP address] "
"(unsafe)`."
msgstr ""
"Selama sertifikat belum diimpor, halaman peringatan muncul saat mencoba "
"mengakses beranda mesin. Lewati dengan mengklik :guilabel:`Advanced` lalu "
":guilabel:`Proceed to [IP address] (unsafe)`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:36
msgid ""
"From the Glory homepage, go to :guilabel:`Host Configuration` and ensure "
"the :guilabel:`Network` setting is set to :guilabel:`MANUAL`, meaning the IP "
"address is static."
msgstr ""
"Dari beranda Glory, buka :guilabel:`Host Configuration` dan pastikan "
"pengaturan :guilabel:`Network` diatur ke :guilabel:`MANUAL`, yang berarti "
"alamat IP bersifat statis."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:38
msgid ""
"Then, navigate to :guilabel:`SSL Configuration` and scroll down to "
"the :guilabel:`HTTPS Server Setting` section."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, navigasikan ke :guilabel:`SSL Configuration` dan gulir ke bawah ke "
"bagian :guilabel:`HTTPS Server Setting`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:41
msgid ""
"In parallel, open the terminal and verify that *OpenSSL* is installed. Type "
"`openssl` and press enter. If installed, this command displays a `help` menu "
"listing all available OpenSSL commands. If nothing happens, `install it "
"<https://openssl-library.org/source/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Secara paralel, buka terminal dan verifikasi bahwa *OpenSSL* sudah "
"terinstal. Ketik `openssl` dan tekan enter. Jika terinstal, perintah ini "
"menampilkan menu `help` yang mencantumkan semua perintah OpenSSL yang "
"tersedia. Jika tidak ada yang terjadi, `install it <https://openssl-"
"library.org/source/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:44
msgid ""
"Then, paste the following command and press `Enter` to generate and download "
"the certificate and private key. Ensure that you replace the demo IP address "
"with the cash machine’s actual IP address."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, tempelkan perintah berikut dan tekan `Enter` untuk menghasilkan "
"dan mengunduh sertifikat dan kunci privat. Pastikan Anda mengganti alamat IP "
"demo dengan alamat IP aktual mesin uang tunai."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:53
msgid ""
"The self-signed SSL certificate and key pair must use the same static IP "
"address as the cash machine."
msgstr ""
"Sertifikat SSL yang ditandatangani sendiri dan pasangan kunci harus "
"menggunakan alamat IP statis yang sama dengan mesin uang tunai."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:56
msgid ""
"Once the files are generated, from the :guilabel:`HTTPS Server Setting` "
"section, upload `cert.pem` as the :guilabel:`Certificate` and `key.pem` as "
"the :guilabel:`Private Key`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah file dibuat, dari bagian :guilabel:`HTTPS Server Setting`, unggah "
"`cert.pem` sebagai :guilabel:`Certificate` dan `key.pem` sebagai "
":guilabel:`Private Key`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:58
msgid ""
"Go to :guilabel:`WebApp Configuration` and ensure the :guilabel:`Interface` "
"setting from the :guilabel:`A: Nodejs Setting` section is set "
"to :guilabel:`Enable`."
msgstr ""
"Buka :guilabel:`WebApp Configuration` dan pastikan pengaturan "
":guilabel:`Interface` dari bagian :guilabel:`A: Nodejs Setting` diatur ke "
":guilabel:`Enable`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:60
msgid "Then, adjust the following settings depending on the POS setup:"
msgstr "Kemudian, sesuaikan pengaturan berikut tergantung pada konfigurasi POS:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:62
msgid ""
"If **multiple POS** are connected to the same cash machine, go "
"to :guilabel:`App Configuration`, scroll down to the :guilabel:`SOAP IF "
"Setting`, and ensure :guilabel:`Session mode` and :guilabel:`Occupy mode` "
"are both set to :guilabel:`Enable`."
msgstr ""
"Jika **beberapa POS** terhubung ke mesin uang tunai yang sama, buka "
":guilabel:`App Configuration`, gulir ke bawah ke :guilabel:`SOAP IF "
"Setting`, dan pastikan :guilabel:`Session mode` dan :guilabel:`Occupy mode` "
"keduanya diatur ke :guilabel:`Enable`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:65
msgid ""
"If **a dedicated user** has been set up on the cash machine for Odoo, which "
"is recommended, go to :guilabel:`App Configuration`, scroll down to "
"the :guilabel:`SOAP IF Setting` section, and :guilabel:`Enable` "
"the :guilabel:`User check` setting."
msgstr ""
"Jika **user khusus** telah diatur pada mesin kas untuk Odoo, yang "
"direkomendasikan, buka :guilabel:`Konfigurasi Aplikasi`, gulir ke bawah ke "
"bagian :guilabel:`Pengaturan SOAP IF`, dan :guilabel:`Aktifkan` pengaturan "
":guilabel:`Pemeriksaan user`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:68
msgid "Restart the cash machine to apply the new settings."
msgstr "Restart mesin uang tunai untuk menerapkan pengaturan baru."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:71
msgid ""
"As this setup is complex and may involve advanced knowledge of Glory "
"hardware, it is advisable to consult the Glory integration partner for "
"configuration if there is any uncertainty."
msgstr ""
"Karena konfigurasi ini kompleks dan mungkin melibatkan pengetahuan lanjutan "
"tentang perangkat keras Glory, disarankan untuk berkonsultasi dengan mitra "
"integrasi Glory untuk konfigurasi jika ada keraguan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:75
msgid "Import self-signed certificates"
msgstr "Impor sertifikat yang ditandatangani sendiri"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:77
msgid ""
"For a long-term solution, the generated certificates must be imported into "
"the device running the POS. The import process is heavily dependent on "
"the :abbr:`OS (Operating System)` and the browser."
msgstr ""
"Untuk solusi jangka panjang, sertifikat yang dihasilkan harus diimpor ke "
"perangkat yang menjalankan POS. Proses impor sangat bergantung pada "
":abbr:`OS (Operating System)` dan browser."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:82
msgid "Windows OS"
msgstr "OS Windows"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:84
msgid ""
"Windows manages certificates, which means that self-signed certificates must "
