msgid ""
"Create a QFPay account on the `QFPay website <https://qfpay.global/products/"
"qfpay-pos-api/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Buat akun QFPay di `situs web QFPay <https://qfpay.global/products/qfpay-pos-"
"api/>`_."

