msgstr ""
"Buat :guilabel:`POS-KEY` dari Aplikasi HaoJin: buka :menuselection:`Aplikasi "
"Haojin --> My --> Settings --> Pos Call Up Key --> Reset Key`. Kemudian, "
"salin :guilabel:`POS-KEY` yang dihasilkan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/qfpay.rst:33
msgid ""
"The **Asynchronous Notifications** are automated messages confirming "
"successful payments or refunds by QFPay."
msgstr ""
"**Notifikasi Asinkron** adalah pesan otomatis yang mengonfirmasi "
