msgid ""
"If the terminal's IP address changes, update it in the :ref:`Odoo POS "
"settings <pos/use/settings>` and request a new self-signed certificate from "
"QFPay."
msgstr ""
"Jika alamat IP terminal berubah, perbarui di :ref:`pengaturan Odoo POS <pos/"
"use/settings>` dan minta sertifikat self-signed baru dari QFPay."

