#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:26
msgid "POS product categories"
msgstr "Kategori produk POS"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:28
msgid ""
"POS product categories are used to organize products in the POS register."
msgstr "Kategori produk POS digunakan untuk mengatur produk di kasir POS."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:30
msgid "To manage POS categories, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Untuk mengelola kategori POS, ikuti langkah-langkah berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:32
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Configuration --> PoS Product "
"Categories`."
msgstr ""
"Navigasi ke :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Configuration --> PoS Product "
"Categories`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:33
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`New` to create a category or click an existing one to "
"update it."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`New` untuk membuat kategori atau klik kategori yang sudah "
"ada untuk memperbaruinya."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:34
msgid ""
"Classify and build a hierarchy between categories: Associate a category with "
"a parent category by filling in the :guilabel:`Parent Category` field. A "
"parent category groups one or more child categories (e.g., use `Drinks` to "
"group `Hot beverages` and `Soft drinks`)."
msgstr ""
"Klasifikasikan dan bangun hierarki antara kategori: Kaitkan kategori dengan "
"kategori induk dengan mengisi kolom :guilabel:`Parent Category`. Kategori "
"induk mengelompokkan satu atau lebih kategori anak (misalnya, gunakan "
"`Drinks` untuk mengelompokkan `Hot beverages` dan `Soft drinks`)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:38
msgid ""
"Once POS product categories are created, assign them to specific products:"
msgstr "Setelah kategori produk POS dibuat, tetapkan ke produk tertentu:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:40
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Products --> Products` and open a "
"product form."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Products --> Products` dan buka "
"formulir produk."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:41
msgid ""
"Navigate to the :guilabel:`Point of Sale` tab and fill in "
"the :guilabel:`Category` field with one or multiple POS categories."
msgstr ""
"Navigasi ke tab :guilabel:`Point of Sale` dan isi kolom :guilabel:`Category` "
"dengan satu atau beberapa kategori POS."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:44
msgid ""
"To limit the categories displayed on the POS register, navigate to "
"the :ref:`POS settings <pos/use/settings>` and select the relevant "
"categories in the :guilabel:`Restrict Categories` field under "
"the :guilabel:`Product & PoS categories` section."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membatasi kategori yang ditampilkan pada register POS, navigasi ke "
":ref:`pengaturan POS <pos/use/settings>` dan pilih kategori yang relevan "
"pada kolom :guilabel:`Restrict Categories` di bawah bagian "
":guilabel:`Product & PoS categories`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:51
msgid "Product combos"
msgstr "Kombo produk"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:53
msgid ""
"A product combo is a bundle of multiple products sold together as a unit. "
"Each product combo consists of multiple categories, known as :ref:`combo "
"choices <pos/products/combo-choices>`, and each combo choice contains "
"several items. When purchasing a product combo, customers can select one or "
"more items from each combo choice."
msgstr ""
"Kombo produk adalah bundel beberapa produk yang dijual bersama sebagai satu "
"unit. Setiap kombo produk terdiri dari beberapa kategori, yang dikenal "
"sebagai :ref:`pilihan kombo <pos/products/combo-choices>`, dan setiap "
"pilihan kombo berisi beberapa item. Saat membeli kombo produk, pelanggan "
"dapat memilih satu atau lebih item dari setiap pilihan kombo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:59
msgid ""
"A burger menu is offered as a product combo including three combo choices: "
"one burger, one drink, and one portion of fries. For each combo choice, "
"customers select one item from the available options (e.g., cheeseburger or "
"chicken burger; soda or water; regular or large fries)."
msgstr ""
"Menu burger ditawarkan sebagai kombo produk yang mencakup tiga pilihan "
"kombo: satu burger, satu minuman, dan satu porsi kentang goreng. Untuk "
"setiap pilihan kombo, pelanggan memilih satu item dari opsi yang tersedia "
"(misalnya, burger keju atau burger ayam; soda atau air; kentang goreng "
"regular atau besar)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:64
msgid ""
"`Product combos (video tutorial) <https://youtu.be/H8e2CakLhaQ?"
"si=yjPbvYkj00K7OP3q>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Kombo produk (tutorial video) <https://youtu.be/"
"H8e2CakLhaQ?si=yjPbvYkj00K7OP3q>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:69
msgid "Combo choice creation"
msgstr "Pembuatan pilihan kombo"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:71
msgid ""
"To create the combo choices that will be added to the :ref:`product combo "
"<pos/products/combo-creation>`, follow the next steps:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat pilihan kombo yang akan ditambahkan ke :ref:`kombo produk <pos/"
"products/combo-creation>`, ikuti langkah-langkah berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:74
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Products --> Combo Choices` and "
"click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Produk --> Pilihan Kombo` dan klik "
":guilabel:`Baru`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:75
msgid "Enter a name for the :guilabel:`Combo Choice`."
msgstr "Masukkan nama untuk :guilabel:`Pilihan Kombo`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:76
msgid ""
"Set the maximum selectable items for the combo choice using "
"the :guilabel:`Maximum items` field."
msgstr ""
"Atur jumlah maksimal item yang dapat dipilih untuk pilihan kombo menggunakan "
"kolom :guilabel:`Item maksimal`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:77
msgid ""
"Set the number of items included in the combo choice using "
"the :guilabel:`Includes items` field."
msgstr ""
"Atur jumlah item yang termasuk dalam pilihan kombo menggunakan kolom "
":guilabel:`Termasuk item`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:78
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Add a line` under the :guilabel:`Options` section to add "
"the products that constitute the :guilabel:`Combo Choices`."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Tambahkan baris` di bawah bagian :guilabel:`Opsi` untuk "
"menambahkan produk yang membentuk :guilabel:`Pilihan Kombo`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:80
msgid "If needed, click a product to add an :guilabel:`Extra Price`."
msgstr ""
"Jika diperlukan, klik produk untuk menambahkan :guilabel:`Harga Tambahan`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:82
msgid "Combo Price vs. Extra Price"
msgstr "Harga Kombo vs. Harga Tambahan"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:84
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Combo Price` field shows the price applied to any additional "
"product a customer might select (i.e., when the :guilabel:`Maximum items` "
"field is set to `2` or higher). This price is automatically calculated based "
"on the price of the least expensive product defined in the :guilabel:`Combo "
"Choice`."
msgstr ""
"Kolom :guilabel:`Harga Kombo` menampilkan harga yang diterapkan untuk setiap "
"produk tambahan yang mungkin dipilih pelanggan (yaitu, ketika kolom "
":guilabel:`Item maksimal` diatur ke `2` atau lebih tinggi). Harga ini secara "
"otomatis dihitung berdasarkan harga produk termurah yang ditetapkan dalam "
":guilabel:`Pilihan Kombo`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:88
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Extra Price` field is used to set an additional charge for a "
"specific product in the combo choice, e.g., to cover higher costs or "
"encourage upselling. This extra price is applied each time a customer "
"selects that product within the combo choice."
msgstr ""
"Kolom :guilabel:`Harga Tambahan` digunakan untuk menetapkan biaya tambahan "
"untuk produk tertentu dalam pilihan kombo, misalnya, untuk menutupi biaya "
"lebih tinggi atau mendorong upselling. Harga tambahan ini diterapkan setiap "
"kali pelanggan memilih produk tersebut dalam pilihan kombo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:95
msgid "Product combo creation"
msgstr "Pembuatan kombo produk"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:97
msgid ""
"To create a specific product that contains :ref:`combo choices <pos/products/"
