#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:222
msgid ""
"To define the number of orders visible on a page, click `1-x / x`. Enter a "
"number lower than the total number of pages, and click :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menentukan jumlah pesanan yang terlihat di halaman, klik `1-x / x`. "
"Masukkan angka yang lebih rendah dari jumlah total halaman, dan klik "
":guilabel:`Konfirmasi`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:224
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-trash` (:guilabel:`trash`) icon next to "
"an :guilabel:`Active` order to delete it."
msgstr ""
"Klik ikon :icon:`fa-trash` (:guilabel:`tempat sampah`) di samping pesanan "
":guilabel:`Aktif` untuk menghapusnya."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:226
msgid ""
"If using :doc:`presets <extra/presets>`, click one to view the related "
"orders. Click it again to return to the main overview."
msgstr ""
"Jika menggunakan :doc:`preset <extra/presets>`, klik salah satu untuk "
"melihat pesanan terkait. Klik lagi untuk kembali ke tampilan utama."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:232
msgid "Return and refund products"
msgstr "Kembalikan dan refund produk"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:234
msgid ""
"The steps to process a refund from the :ref:`POS register <pos/use/open-"
"register>` depend on whether the refund is :ref:`based on an order <pos/use/"
"refund-order-based>` or processed as a :ref:`standalone refund that is not "
"based on an order <pos/use/refund-standalone>`."
msgstr ""
"Langkah-langkah untuk memproses pengembalian dana dari\\ :ref:`register POS "
"<pos/use/open-register>`\\ bergantung pada apakah pengembalian dana "
"tersebut\\ :ref:`berdasarkan pesanan <pos/use/refund-order-based>`\\ atau "
"diproses sebagai\\ :ref:`pengembalian dana mandiri yang tidak berdasarkan "
"pesanan <pos/use/refund-standalone>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:238
msgid ""
"In both cases, the amount can be refunded or a :ref:`gift card <pos/pricing/"
"loyalty>` issued for the refunded amount."
msgstr ""
"Dalam kedua kasus, jumlahnya dapat dikembalikan atau\\ :ref:`kartu hadiah "
"<pos/pricing/loyalty>`\\ diterbitkan untuk jumlah yang dikembalikan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:242
msgid ""
"Once the return is validated, a corresponding credit note is generated, "
"referencing the original :doc:`receipt <use/receipts>` or :doc:`invoice <use/"
"pos_invoices>`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah pengembalian divalidasi, nota kredit yang sesuai akan dibuat, dengan "
"referensi ke :doc:`tanda terima <use/receipts>` atau :doc:`faktur <use/"
"pos_invoices>` asli."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:246
msgid ":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/credit_notes`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/credit_notes`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:251
msgid "Order-based refunds"
msgstr "Pengembalian dana berdasarkan pesanan"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:253
msgid "To process a refund based on an order, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk memproses pengembalian dana berdasarkan pesanan, ikuti langkah-langkah "
"berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:255
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`vertical ellipsis`) icon in the "
"POS register."
msgstr ""
"Klik ikon\\ :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v`\\ (:guilabel:`elipsis vertikal`) di "
"register POS."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:256
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`Refund`. The orders overview opens, displaying "
"all :guilabel:`Paid` orders."
msgstr ""
"Pilih\\ :guilabel:`Refund`. Ikhtisar pesanan terbuka, menampilkan semua "
"pesanan\\ :guilabel:`Paid`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:257
msgid ""
"Select the product(s) to refund, and then enter the quantity to refund if "
"needed."
msgstr ""
"Pilih produk yang akan dikembalikan, lalu masukkan jumlah yang akan "
"dikembalikan jika diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:258
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Refund` to open the payment screen."
msgstr "Klik\\ :guilabel:`Refund`\\ untuk membuka layar pembayaran."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:259
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:287
msgid "Choose how to handle the refund:"
msgstr "Pilih cara menangani pengembalian dana:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:261
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:289
msgid ""
"To refund the customer, on the payment screen, select a payment method, then "
"click :guilabel:`Validate`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengembalikan dana kepada pelanggan, pada layar pembayaran, pilih "
"metode pembayaran, lalu klik\\ :guilabel:`Validate`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:263
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:291
msgid ""
"To issue a :ref:`gift card <pos/pricing/loyalty>` for the refund amount, on "
"the payment screen, click :guilabel:`Back`. The cart displays the returned "
"product(s) with a negative quantity. Then, add the gift card from the "
"product selector to the order; its value is automatically set to match the "
"total refund amount. Click :guilabel:`Payment`, then :guilabel:`Validate` "
"the refund."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menerbitkan\\ :ref:`kartu hadiah <pos/pricing/loyalty>`\\ untuk jumlah "
"pengembalian dana, pada layar pembayaran, klik\\ :guilabel:`Back`. Keranjang "
"menampilkan produk yang dikembalikan dengan jumlah negatif. Kemudian, "
"tambahkan kartu hadiah dari pemilih produk ke pesanan; nilainya secara "
"otomatis disetel agar sesuai dengan jumlah pengembalian dana total. Klik\\ "
":guilabel:`Payment`, lalu\\ :guilabel:`Validate`\\ pengembalian dana."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:270
msgid ""
"Alternatively, access the list of paid orders by clicking :guilabel:`Orders` "
"in the POS interface header and selecting :guilabel:`Paid` from "
"the :guilabel:`Active` dropdown menu."
msgstr ""
"Atau, akses daftar pesanan yang dibayar dengan mengklik\\ "
":guilabel:`Orders`\\ di header antarmuka POS dan memilih\\ :guilabel:`Paid`\\"
" dari menu dropdown\\ :guilabel:`Active`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:272
msgid ""
"Refunds can also be initiated and processed from the backend. To do so, go "
"to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Orders --> Orders`, select an order, "
"then click :guilabel:`Return Products`. Note that this method can only be "
"used to refund the entire order."
msgstr ""
"Pengembalian dana juga dapat dimulai dan diproses dari backend. Untuk "
"melakukannya, buka\\ :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Orders --> Orders`, "
"pilih pesanan, lalu klik\\ :guilabel:`Return Products`. Perhatikan bahwa "
"metode ini hanya dapat digunakan untuk mengembalikan dana seluruh pesanan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:279
msgid "Standalone refunds"
msgstr "Pengembalian dana mandiri"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:281
msgid ""
"To process a standalone refund that is *not* based on an order, follow these "
"steps:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk memproses pengembalian dana mandiri yang *tidak* berdasarkan pesanan, "
"ikuti langkah-langkah berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:283
msgid "Select the relevant product from the POS register."
msgstr "Pilih produk yang relevan dari register POS."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:284
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Qty` to enter the quantity to refund, then "
"click :guilabel:`+/-` to set it as a negative quantity."
msgstr ""
"Klik\\ :guilabel:`Qty`\\ untuk memasukkan jumlah yang akan dikembalikan, "
"lalu klik\\ :guilabel:`+/-`\\ untuk menetapkannya sebagai jumlah negatif."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:286
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Payment` to open the payment screen."
msgstr "Klik\\ :guilabel:`Payment`\\ untuk membuka layar pembayaran."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:298
msgid ""
"To facilitate management of standalone returns, create a :doc:`preset <extra/"
"presets>` with only the :guilabel:`Return mode` enabled. When this preset is "
"selected from the POS register, the quantity of any item added to the cart "
"is set to negative."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memfasilitasi pengelolaan pengembalian mandiri, buat\\ :doc:`preset "
"<extra/presets>`\\ dengan hanya\\ :guilabel:`Return mode`\\ yang diaktifkan. "
"Ketika preset ini dipilih dari register POS, jumlah item apa pun yang "
"ditambahkan ke keranjang disetel ke negatif."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:305
msgid "Add and manage notes"
msgstr "Tambahkan dan kelola catatan"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:307
msgid ""
"Notes allow for extra information to be added to specific products in an "
"order. There are two types of notes: :ref:`internal notes <pos/use/internal-"
"notes>` and :ref:`customer notes <pos/use/customer-notes>`."
msgstr ""
"Catatan memungkinkan informasi tambahan ditambahkan ke produk tertentu dalam "
"pesanan. Ada dua jenis catatan:\\ :ref:`catatan internal <pos/use/internal-"
"notes>`\\ dan\\ :ref:`catatan pelanggan <pos/use/customer-notes>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:312
msgid ""
"If the same content is frequently used, configure a note model to save time. "
"To create or edit note models, go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> "
"Configuration --> Note Models`, click :guilabel:`New` or click the relevant "
"note model, then complete or edit the :guilabel:`Name` column."
msgstr ""
"Jika konten yang sama sering digunakan, konfigurasikan model catatan untuk "
"menghemat waktu. Untuk membuat atau mengedit model catatan, buka "
":menuselection:`POS --> Konfigurasi --> Model Catatan`, klik "
":guilabel:`Baru` atau klik model catatan yang relevan, lalu lengkapi atau "
"edit kolom :guilabel:`Nama`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:318
msgid ""
"Any customer notes added to a product from the :ref:`POS register <pos/use/"
"open-register>` are displayed on the :doc:`customer display <../"
"point_of_sale/hardware_network/customer_display>`."
msgstr ""
"Setiap catatan pelanggan yang ditambahkan ke produk dari :ref:`kasir POS "
"<pos/use/open-register>` ditampilkan pada :doc:`layar pelanggan <../"
"point_of_sale/hardware_network/customer_display>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:324
msgid "Internal notes"
msgstr "Catatan internal"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:326
msgid ""
"Internal notes provide information intended for staff (e.g., `no tomato` for "
"the kitchen team) and do not appear on the customer's receipt."
msgstr ""
"Catatan internal memberikan informasi yang ditujukan untuk staf (misalnya, "
"`tanpa tomat` untuk tim dapur) dan tidak muncul pada struk pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:329
msgid ""
"To add or edit an internal note from the POS register, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan atau mengedit catatan internal dari kasir POS, ikuti "
"langkah-langkah berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:331
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:349
msgid "If the note applies to:"
msgstr "Jika catatan berlaku untuk:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:333
msgid ""
"The entire order: Ensure no item is selected in the cart, then "
"click :guilabel:`Note`."
msgstr ""
"Seluruh pesanan: Pastikan tidak ada item yang dipilih di keranjang, lalu "
"klik :guilabel:`Catatan`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:334
msgid ""
"A specific item: Select the item in the cart, then click :guilabel:`Note`."
msgstr "Item tertentu: Pilih item di keranjang, lalu klik :guilabel:`Catatan`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:335
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:355
msgid ""
"Add or modify the note's content in the popover or select a previously "
"configured note model."
msgstr ""
"Tambahkan atau ubah konten catatan di popover atau pilih model catatan yang "
"telah dikonfigurasi sebelumnya."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:336
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:356
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Apply`."
msgstr "Klik :guilabel:`Terapkan`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:341
msgid "Customer notes"
msgstr "Catatan pelanggan"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:343
msgid ""
"Customer notes appear on :doc:`receipts <use/receipts>` and :doc:`invoices "
"<use/pos_invoices>`. They can be used, for example, to provide warranty "
"details for a high-value item or specific care instructions, such as `Dry "
"clean only`."
msgstr ""
"Catatan pelanggan muncul pada :doc:`struk <use/receipts>` dan :doc:`faktur "
"<use/pos_invoices>`. Catatan ini dapat digunakan, misalnya, untuk memberikan "
"detail garansi untuk barang bernilai tinggi atau instruksi perawatan khusus, "
"seperti `Hanya dry clean`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:347
msgid ""
"To add or edit a customer note from the POS register, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan atau mengedit catatan pelanggan dari kasir POS, ikuti "
"langkah-langkah berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:351
msgid ""
"The entire order: Ensure no item is selected in the cart, click "
"the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`vertical ellipsis`) icon, then "
"click :guilabel:`Customer Note`."
msgstr ""
"Seluruh pesanan: Pastikan tidak ada item yang dipilih di keranjang, klik "
"ikon :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`ellipsis vertikal`), lalu klik "
":guilabel:`Catatan Pelanggan`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:353
msgid ""
"A specific item: Select the item in the cart, click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-"
"v` (:guilabel:`vertical ellipsis`) icon, then click :guilabel:`Customer "
"Note`."
msgstr ""
"Item tertentu: Pilih item di keranjang, klik ikon :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` "
"(:guilabel:`ellipsis vertikal`), lalu klik :guilabel:`Catatan Pelanggan`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:359
msgid ""
"Product notes from :ref:`imported sales orders <pos/shop/so>` are displayed "
"in the same way as customer notes."
msgstr ""
"Catatan produk dari :ref:`pesanan penjualan yang diimpor <pos/shop/so>` "
"ditampilkan dengan cara yang sama seperti catatan pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:None
msgid ""
"Customer note button and notes (SO and POS register) on products in the cart"
msgstr ""
"Tombol catatan pelanggan dan catatan (SO dan register POS) pada produk di "
"keranjang"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:368
msgid "Manage the cash register"
msgstr "Kelola mesin kasir"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:370
msgid ""
"Odoo POS allows accepted coins and bills to be defined. To set up the "
"allowed coins and bills:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo POS memungkinkan koin dan uang kertas yang diterima untuk "
"didefinisikan. Untuk mengatur koin dan uang kertas yang diizinkan:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:372
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Configuration --> Coins/Bills`."
msgstr "Buka :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Configuration --> Coins/Bills`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:373
msgid "Click :guilabel:`New` to add a new value."
msgstr "Klik :guilabel:`Baru` untuk menambahkan nilai baru."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:374
msgid ""
"Select the POS where this value is accepted in the :guilabel:`Point of "
"Sales` column, or leave the field empty to make it available for all POS."
msgstr ""
"Pilih POS tempat nilai ini diterima di kolom :guilabel:`Point of Sales`, "
"atau biarkan kolom kosong untuk membuatnya tersedia untuk semua POS."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:377
msgid ""
"To record a cash-in or cash-out transaction not associated with a sale from "
"the POS register:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk mencatat transaksi pemasukan kas atau pengeluaran kas yang tidak "
"terkait dengan penjualan dari kasir POS:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:379
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-bars` (:guilabel:`hamburger menu`) icon on the POS "
"interface."
msgstr ""
"Klik ikon :icon:`fa-bars` (:guilabel:`menu hamburger`) pada antarmuka POS."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:380
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Cash In/Out`."
msgstr "Klik :guilabel:`Masuk/Keluar Kas`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:381
msgid "Select :guilabel:`Cash In` or :guilabel:`Cash Out` in the popover."
msgstr ""
"Pilih :guilabel:`Pemasukan Kas` atau :guilabel:`Pengeluaran Kas` di popover."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:382
msgid "Enter the amount in the field with the currency symbol."
msgstr "Masukkan jumlah di kolom dengan simbol mata uang."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:383
msgid ""
"Specify the reason for the addition or removal of cash, and "
"click :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr ""
"Tentukan alasan penambahan atau pengurangan kas, lalu klik "
":guilabel:`Konfirmasi`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:386
msgid ""
"Only employees with :ref:`basic or advanced access rights <pos/"
"employee_login/configuration>` are allowed to perform cash-in/out actions."
msgstr ""
"Hanya karyawan dengan :ref:`hak akses dasar atau lanjutan <pos/"
"employee_login/configuration>` yang diizinkan untuk melakukan tindakan cash-"
"in/out."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:392
msgid "Close the POS register"
msgstr "Tutup register POS"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:394
msgid ""
"To close the POS register, click the :icon:`fa-bars` (:guilabel:`hamburger "
"menu`) icon, then :guilabel:`Close Register`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menutup register POS, klik ikon :icon:`fa-bars` (:guilabel:`menu "
"hamburger`), lalu :guilabel:`Tutup Register`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:397
msgid "The :guilabel:`Closing Register` popover displays:"
msgstr "Popover :guilabel:`Closing Register` menampilkan:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:399
msgid "The number of orders and the total amount made during the session."
msgstr "Jumlah pesanan dan total nilai yang dibuat selama sesi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:400
msgid "The expected amounts grouped by payment method."
msgstr "Jumlah yang diharapkan dikelompokkan berdasarkan metode pembayaran."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:402
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-money` (:guilabel:`money`) icon to specify the number of "
"coins and bills, then click :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr ""
"Klik ikon :icon:`fa-money` (:guilabel:`money`) untuk menentukan jumlah koin "
"dan uang kertas, kemudian klik :guilabel:`Confirm`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:405
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Close Register` to close the register and post accounting "
"entries."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Tutup Register` untuk menutup register dan memposting entri "
"akuntansi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:408
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-clone` (:guilabel:`clone`) icon to automatically fill in "
"the field with the expected cash amount."
msgstr ""
"Klik ikon :icon:`fa-clone` (:guilabel:`clone`) untuk mengisi kolom secara "
"otomatis dengan jumlah kas yang diharapkan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:412
msgid ""
"After specifying the number of coins and bills, the computed amount is set "
"in the :guilabel:`Cash Count` field, and the :guilabel:`Closing details` are "
"specified in the :guilabel:`Closing note` section."
msgstr ""
"Setelah menentukan jumlah koin dan uang kertas, jumlah yang dihitung diatur "
"dalam kolom :guilabel:`Cash Count`, dan :guilabel:`Closing details` "
"ditentukan di bagian :guilabel:`Closing note`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:415
msgid ""
"Closing the register of a :doc:`restaurant <restaurant>` POS when orders are "
"still in draft and not scheduled for later is not allowed and opens a "
"popover with options to :guilabel:`Review Orders` or :guilabel:`Cancel "
"Orders`."
msgstr ""
"Menutup register POS :doc:`restoran <restaurant>` ketika pesanan masih dalam "
"bentuk draft dan tidak dijadwalkan untuk nanti tidak diizinkan dan akan "
"membuka popover dengan opsi untuk :guilabel:`Review Orders` atau "
":guilabel:`Cancel Orders`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:418
msgid ""
"It is strongly advised to close the POS register at the end of each day."
msgstr "Sangat disarankan untuk menutup register POS di akhir setiap hari."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:421
msgid "Set maximum difference"
msgstr "Tetapkan perbedaan maksimum"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:423
msgid ""
"When the counted money does **not** match the expected amount, "
"a :guilabel:`Payments Difference` window appears, prompting you to "
"acknowledge the discrepancy. Click :guilabel:`Proceed Anyway` to accept the "
"difference and post it to the designated cash difference journal."
msgstr ""
"Ketika uang yang dihitung **tidak** sesuai dengan jumlah yang diharapkan, "
"jendela :guilabel:`Payments Difference` akan muncul, meminta Anda untuk "
"mengakui perbedaan tersebut. Klik :guilabel:`Proceed Anyway` untuk menerima "
"perbedaan dan mempostingnya ke jurnal perbedaan kas yang ditentukan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:427
msgid ""
"To restrict this behavior, you can prevent users from closing the register "
"when a discrepancy occurs by enabling the :guilabel:`Set Maximum Difference` "
"setting in the :guilabel:`Payment` section of the :ref:`POS settings <pos/"
"use/settings>`. Then, specify the allowed limit in the :guilabel:`Authorized "
"Difference` field."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membatasi perilaku ini, Anda dapat mencegah user menutup register "
"ketika terjadi perbedaan dengan mengaktifkan pengaturan :guilabel:`Set "
"Maximum Difference` di bagian :guilabel:`Payment` pada :ref:`pengaturan POS "
"<pos/use/settings>`. Kemudian, tentukan batas yang diizinkan dalam kolom "
":guilabel:`Authorized Difference`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:432
msgid ""
"Once configured, if a discrepancy exceeds this limit, the pop-up window "
"displays the authorized threshold and instructs the user to contact a "
"manager to approve the closing."
msgstr ""
"Setelah dikonfigurasi, jika perbedaan melebihi batas ini, jendela pop-up "
"akan menampilkan ambang batas yang diizinkan dan menginstruksikan user untuk "
