msgid ""
"Set the :guilabel:`Print` field to :guilabel:`QR code`, :guilabel:`URL`, "
"or :guilabel:`QR code + URL` to determine how customers can access their "
"invoice (e.g., by scanning the QR code or by typing the URL in a browser)."
msgstr ""
"Atur bidang :guilabel:`Cetak` ke :guilabel:`Kode QR`, :guilabel:`URL`, atau "
":guilabel:`Kode QR + URL` untuk menentukan bagaimana pelanggan dapat "
"mengakses faktur mereka (misalnya, dengan memindai kode QR atau dengan "
"mengetik URL di browser)."

