"Aplikasi **Rental** Odoo menyediakan solusi komprehensif untuk "
"mengonfigurasi dan mengelola rental."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental.rst:11
msgid ""
"Send quotations, confirm orders, schedule rentals, register products when "
"they are picked up and returned, and invoice customers from this single "
"platform."
msgstr ""
"Kirim penawaran, konfirmasi pesanan, jadwalkan rental, daftarkan produk saat "
"diambil dan dikembalikan, serta buat faktur pelanggan dari satu platform ini."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental.rst:15
