msgstr "Layanan Rental"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/service_products.rst:61
msgid ""
"To view all products that can be rented in the database, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Rentals app --> Products`. By default, "
"the :guilabel:`Rental` filter appears in the search bar, and the view is "
"Kanban. Remove the filter, then click the search bar. From the preset "
"filters, select :guilabel:`Services`. All the configured services appear."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat semua produk yang dapat disewa dalam database, buka "
":menuselection:`aplikasi Rental --> Products`. Secara default, filter "
":guilabel:`Rental` muncul di bilah pencarian, dan tampilannya adalah Kanban. "
"Hapus filter, lalu klik bilah pencarian. Dari filter yang telah ditetapkan, "
"pilih :guilabel:`Services`. Semua layanan yang dikonfigurasi akan muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/rental/configure_products/service_products.rst:66
msgid "Each Kanban card displays the name and rental price of the service."
msgstr "Setiap kartu Kanban menampilkan nama dan harga sewa layanan."

