#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:35
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Create invoice(s)` pop-up window, the down payment options "
"are:"
msgstr "Pada jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Buat faktur`, opsi uang muka adalah:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:40
msgid ""
"Select a down payment option and set the desired payment, either as a "
"percentage or a fixed amount, in the :guilabel:`Down Payment Amount` field."
msgstr ""
"Pilih opsi down payment dan atur pembayaran yang diinginkan, baik sebagai "
"persentase atau jumlah tetap, di bidang :guilabel:`Down Payment Amount`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:43
msgid ""
"Once all fields are filled in, click the :guilabel:`Create Draft` button. "
"Upon clicking this button, Odoo reveals the :guilabel:`Customer Invoice "
"Draft`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah semua bidang diisi, klik tombol :guilabel:`Buat Draf`. Setelah "
"mengklik tombol ini, Odoo menampilkan :guilabel:`Draf Faktur Pelanggan`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:47
msgid ""
"If an :guilabel:`Invalid Operation` error appears, double-check that "
"the :doc:`invoicing policy <invoicing_policy>` is configured correctly. In "
"some cases, for example, the invoicing policy is configured to require "
"delivery before sending an invoice."
msgstr ""
"Jika kesalahan :guilabel:`Invalid Operation` muncul, periksa kembali bahwa "
":doc:`invoicing policy <invoicing_policy>` dikonfigurasi dengan benar. Dalam "
"beberapa kasus, misalnya, kebijakan penagihan dikonfigurasi untuk memerlukan "
"pengiriman sebelum mengirim faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:51
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` tab of the :guilabel:`Customer Invoice "
"Draft`, the down payment that was just configured in the :guilabel:`Create "
"invoice(s)` pop-up form appears under a new :guilabel:`Down Payments` "
"section."
msgstr ""
"Di tab :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` dari :guilabel:`Customer Invoice Draft`, "
"down payment yang baru saja dikonfigurasi di formulir pop-up "
":guilabel:`Create invoice(s)` muncul di bawah bagian :guilabel:`Down "
"Payments` yang baru."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:58
msgid "Example: requesting a 50% down payment"
msgstr "Contoh: meminta down payment 50%"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:61
msgid ""
"The following example involves a 50% amount down payment on a "
"(:guilabel:`Cabinet with Doors`) with :guilabel:`Ordered quantities` as "
"the :guilabel:`Invoicing Policy`."
msgstr ""
"Contoh berikut melibatkan down payment jumlah 50% pada (:guilabel:`Cabinet "
"with Doors`) dengan :guilabel:`Ordered quantities` sebagai "
":guilabel:`Invoicing Policy`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:0
msgid "Cabinet with doors product form showcasing various details and fields."
msgstr ""
"Formulir produk lemari dengan pintu yang menampilkan berbagai detail dan "
"bidang."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:67
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app --> New`, and add "
"a :guilabel:`Customer` to the quotation. Then, click :guilabel:`Add a "
"product` in the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab, and select "
"the :guilabel:`Cabinet with Doors` product. When the order is confirmed (via "
"the :guilabel:`Confirm` button), the quotation turns into a sales order. "
"Once this occurs, create and view the invoice by clicking :guilabel:`Create "
"Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Navigasi ke :menuselection:`Sales app --> New`, dan tambahkan "
":guilabel:`Customer` ke penawaran. Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Add a product` "
"di tab :guilabel:`Order Lines`, dan pilih produk :guilabel:`Cabinet with "
"Doors`. Ketika order dikonfirmasi (melalui tombol :guilabel:`Confirm`), "
"penawaran berubah menjadi sales order. Setelah ini terjadi, buat dan lihat "
"faktur dengan mengklik :guilabel:`Create Invoice`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:None
msgid ""
"Cabinet with doors sales order that's been confirmed in the Odoo Sales "
"application."
msgstr ""
"Sales order lemari dengan pintu yang telah dikonfirmasi di aplikasi "
"Penjualan Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:76
msgid ""
"Next, on the :guilabel:`Create invoice(s)` pop-up window that appears, "
"select :guilabel:`Down payment (percentage)`, and type `50` in "
"the :guilabel:`Down Payment` field."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, pada jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Create invoice(s)` yang muncul, "
"pilih :guilabel:`Down payment (percentage)`, dan ketik `50` di bidang "
":guilabel:`Down Payment`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:80
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Income Account` attached to the :guilabel:`Down payment` can "
"be changed. For more information, check out the documentation "
"on :ref:`income account modification on down payments <sales/invoicing/"
"income-account-modification>`. A :guilabel:`Down payment Account` can also "
"be set on a product category. If set, this account is prioritized for future "
"down payments."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Akun Pendapatan` yang terlampir pada :guilabel:`Uang muka` dapat "
"diubah. Untuk informasi lebih lanjut, lihat dokumentasi tentang "
":ref:`modifikasi akun pendapatan pada uang muka <sales/invoicing/income-"
"account-modification>`. :guilabel:`Akun Uang Muka` juga dapat diatur pada "
"kategori produk. Jika diatur, akun ini diprioritaskan untuk uang muka di "
"masa mendatang."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:85
msgid ""
"Lastly, click :guilabel:`Create Draft Invoice` to create and view the "
"invoice draft, which includes the down payment under the :guilabel:`Down "
"Payments` section of the :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` tab. From there, the "
"invoice can be confirmed and posted by clicking :guilabel:`Confirm`. "
"Confirming the invoice changes the status from :guilabel:`Draft` "
"to :guilabel:`Posted`. It also reveals a new series of buttons at the top of "
"the page."
msgstr ""
"Terakhir, klik :guilabel:`Buat Faktur Draft` untuk membuat dan melihat draft "
"faktur, yang mencakup uang muka di bawah bagian :guilabel:`Uang Muka` pada "
"tab :guilabel:`Baris Faktur`. Dari sana, faktur dapat dikonfirmasi dan "
"diposting dengan mengklik :guilabel:`Konfirmasi`. Mengonfirmasi faktur "
"mengubah status dari :guilabel:`Draft` menjadi :guilabel:`Diposting`. Ini "
"juga menampilkan serangkaian tombol baru di bagian atas halaman."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:None
msgid "A sample draft invoice with down payment mentioned in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Contoh draf faktur dengan uang muka yang disebutkan di Penjualan Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:94
msgid ""
"From those buttons, the payment can be registered by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Pay`. Doing so reveals a :guilabel:`Pay` pop-up form, "
"which is auto-populated with the necessary information. Confirm the "
"information provided is correct, and make any necessary adjustments. When "
"ready, click the :guilabel:`Create Payment` button."
msgstr ""
"Dari tombol-tombol tersebut, pembayaran dapat didaftarkan dengan mengklik "
":guilabel:`Bayar`. Melakukan hal ini menampilkan formulir pop-up "
":guilabel:`Bayar`, yang terisi otomatis dengan informasi yang diperlukan. "
"Konfirmasi bahwa informasi yang diberikan sudah benar, dan lakukan "
"penyesuaian yang diperlukan. Ketika siap, klik tombol :guilabel:`Buat "
"Pembayaran`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:None
msgid "Showcase of the Pay pop-up window with create payment button."
msgstr "Tampilan jendela pop-up Bayar dengan tombol buat pembayaran."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:102
msgid ""
"After clicking :guilabel:`Create Payment`, Odoo reveals the customer "
"invoice, now with a green :guilabel:`In Payment` or :guilabel:`Paid` banner "
"in the upper-right corner, depending on how the database has configured and "
"if manual confirmation of payments is required."
msgstr ""
"Setelah mengklik :guilabel:`Buat Pembayaran`, Odoo menampilkan faktur "
"pelanggan, sekarang dengan banner hijau :guilabel:`Dalam Pembayaran` atau "
":guilabel:`Dibayar` di sudut kanan atas, tergantung pada bagaimana database "
"dikonfigurasi dan apakah diperlukan konfirmasi pembayaran manual."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:None
msgid ""
"Customer Invoice with a green Paid banner located in the upper-right corner."
msgstr ""
"Faktur Pelanggan dengan banner hijau Dibayar yang terletak di sudut kanan "
"atas."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:109
msgid ""
"On the sales order, a new :guilabel:`Down Payments` section is present in "
"the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab, along with the down payment that was just "
"invoiced and posted. When the customer wants to pay the remaining amount of "
"the order, another invoice must be created."
msgstr ""
"Pada sales order, bagian :guilabel:`Uang Muka` baru muncul di tab "
":guilabel:`Baris Pesanan`, bersama dengan uang muka yang baru saja difaktur "
"dan diposting. Ketika pelanggan ingin membayar jumlah sisa pesanan, faktur "
"lain harus dibuat."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:None
msgid "The down payments section in the order lines tab of a sales order."
msgstr "Bagian uang muka di tab baris pesanan dari sales order."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:116
msgid ""
"Next, click the :guilabel:`Create Invoice` button. On the :guilabel:`Create "
"invoice(s)` pop-up window that appears, there is a new "
"field: :guilabel:`Already invoiced` and :guilabel:`Amount to invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, klik tombol :guilabel:`Buat Faktur`. Pada jendela pop-up "
":guilabel:`Buat faktur` yang muncul, ada kolom baru: :guilabel:`Sudah "
"difaktur` dan :guilabel:`Jumlah yang akan difaktur`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:None
msgid ""
"The deduct down payment option on the Create invoice(s) pop up in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Opsi potong uang muka pada pop-up Buat faktur di Odoo Sales."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:123
msgid ""
"If the remaining amount is ready to be paid, select the :guilabel:`Regular "
"Invoice` option. Odoo will create an invoice for the exact amount needed to "
"complete the total payment, as indicated in the :guilabel:`Amount to "
"invoice` field."
msgstr ""
"Jika jumlah sisa siap dibayar, pilih opsi :guilabel:`Faktur Reguler`. Odoo "
"akan membuat faktur dengan jumlah tepat yang diperlukan untuk menyelesaikan "
"total pembayaran, seperti yang ditunjukkan di bidang :guilabel:`Jumlah yang "
"akan difakturkan`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:127
msgid ""
"Once ready, click :guilabel:`Create Draft Invoice`. Doing so reveals "
"another :guilabel:`Customer Invoice Draft` page, listing all the invoices "
"for that specific sales order in the :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` tab. Each "
"invoice line item displays all the necessary information related to each "
"invoice."
msgstr ""
"Setelah siap, klik :guilabel:`Buat Faktur Draft`. Melakukan hal ini "
"menampilkan halaman :guilabel:`Draft Faktur Pelanggan` lainnya, yang "
"mencantumkan semua faktur untuk sales order tertentu tersebut di tab "
":guilabel:`Baris Faktur`. Setiap item baris faktur menampilkan semua "
"informasi yang diperlukan terkait setiap faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:132
msgid ""
"To complete the flow, click :guilabel:`Confirm` to change the status of the "
"invoice from :guilabel:`Draft` to :guilabel:`Posted`. Then, "
"click :guilabel:`Pay`. The :guilabel:`Pay` form appears, with all fields "
"auto-populated with the necessary information, including the remaining "
"amount left to be paid on the order."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menyelesaikan alur, klik :guilabel:`Konfirmasi` untuk mengubah status "
"faktur dari :guilabel:`Draft` menjadi :guilabel:`Diposting`. Kemudian, klik "
":guilabel:`Bayar`. Formulir :guilabel:`Bayar` muncul, dengan semua kolom "
"terisi otomatis dengan informasi yang diperlukan, termasuk jumlah sisa yang "
"harus dibayar pada pesanan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:None
msgid "The second Pay pop-up form in Odoo sales."
msgstr "Formulir pop-up Bayar kedua di Odoo sales."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:140
msgid ""
"After confirming that information, click :guilabel:`Create Payment`. Doing "
"so reveals the final :guilabel:`Customer Invoice` with a green :guilabel:`In "
"Payment` or :guilabel:`Paid` banner in the upper-right corner, depending on "
"how the database has configured and if manual confirmation of payments is "
"required. Upon returning to the sales order, both down payments are present "
"in the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab."
msgstr ""
"Setelah mengonfirmasi informasi tersebut, klik :guilabel:`Buat Pembayaran`. "
"Melakukan hal ini menampilkan :guilabel:`Faktur Pelanggan` final dengan "
"banner hijau :guilabel:`Dalam Pembayaran` atau :guilabel:`Dibayar` di sudut "
"kanan atas, tergantung pada bagaimana database dikonfigurasi dan apakah "
"diperlukan konfirmasi pembayaran manual. Setelah kembali ke sales order, "
"kedua uang muka muncul di tab :guilabel:`Baris Pesanan`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:None
msgid "The second down payment invoice with Paid banner in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Faktur uang muka kedua dengan banner Dibayar di Odoo Sales."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:149
msgid ""
"At this point, the flow is now complete. This flow is also possible with "
"the :guilabel:`Fixed amount` down payment option."
msgstr ""
"Pada titik ini, alur sekarang selesai. Alur ini juga dimungkinkan dengan "
"opsi uang muka :guilabel:`Jumlah tetap`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:153
msgid ""
"If a down payment is used with a product that has a :guilabel:`Delivered "
"quantities` invoicing policy, and the cost of the product exceeds the 50% "
"down payment, a regular invoice is created. However, for products that cost "
"less than the 50% down payment, the down payments will not be able to be "
"deducted when it comes time to invoice the customer. This is because the "
"product(s) would have to be delivered *before* creating the final invoice "
"due to Odoo not allowing negative totals for invoices. If nothing has been "
"delivered, a :guilabel:`Credit Note` is created, which cancels the draft "
"invoice that was created after the down payment."
msgstr ""
"Jika uang muka digunakan dengan produk yang memiliki kebijakan penagihan "
":guilabel:`Kuantitas terkirim`, dan biaya produk melebihi uang muka 50%, "
"faktur reguler dibuat. Namun, untuk produk yang biayanya kurang dari uang "
"muka 50%, uang muka tidak akan dapat dipotong ketika saatnya menagih "
"pelanggan. Ini karena produk harus dikirim *sebelum* membuat faktur final "
"karena Odoo tidak mengizinkan total negatif untuk faktur. Jika tidak ada "
"yang dikirim, :guilabel:`Nota Kredit` dibuat, yang membatalkan draft faktur "
"yang dibuat setelah uang muka."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:161
msgid ""
"To utilize the :guilabel:`Credit Note` option, the **Inventory** application "
"must be installed in order to confirm the delivery. Otherwise, the delivered "
"quantity can be entered manually directly on the sales order."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menggunakan opsi :guilabel:`Nota Kredit`, aplikasi **Inventaris** "
"harus diinstal untuk mengonfirmasi pengiriman. Jika tidak, kuantitas "
"terkirim dapat dimasukkan secara manual langsung pada sales order."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:168
msgid "Example: requesting a 100% down payment"
msgstr "Contoh: meminta uang muka 100%"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:170
msgid ""
"Requesting a 100% down payment is similar to requesting a :ref:`50% down "
"payment <sales/invoicing/50-percent-down-payments>`, but with fewer steps."
msgstr ""
"Meminta uang muka 100% mirip dengan meminta :ref:`uang muka 50% <sales/"
"invoicing/50-percent-down-payments>`, tetapi dengan langkah yang lebih "
"sedikit."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:174
msgid ""
"A 100% down payment is not the same as a full payment of the sales order. A "
"sales order paid through the regular invoice process will not allow any "
"additional invoices to be generated and will not display "
"the :guilabel:`Create Invoice` button on the Sales Order. Instead, following "
"this example will cause the :guilabel:`Create Invoice` button to be "
"displayed on the Sales Order. This is because the system expects another "
"invoice to be created after the down payment to complete payment of the "
"sales order."
msgstr ""
"Uang muka 100% tidak sama dengan pembayaran penuh sales order. Sales order "
"yang dibayar melalui proses faktur reguler tidak akan mengizinkan faktur "
"tambahan dibuat dan tidak akan menampilkan tombol :guilabel:`Buat Faktur` "
"pada Sales Order. Sebaliknya, mengikuti contoh ini akan menyebabkan tombol "
":guilabel:`Buat Faktur` ditampilkan pada Sales Order. Ini karena sistem "
"mengharapkan faktur lain dibuat setelah uang muka untuk menyelesaikan "
"pembayaran sales order."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:181
msgid "The *Solar Panel Installation* product is being used in this example."
msgstr "Produk *Instalasi Panel Surya* digunakan dalam contoh ini."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:183
msgid ""
"To configure a 100% down payment, navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app --> "
"New` and add a :guilabel:`Customer` to the quote. Next, click :guilabel:`Add "
"a product` in the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab, and select the `Solar Panel "
"Installation` product. Upon clicking the :guilabel:`Confirm` button, the "
"quotation turns into a sales order. At that point, an invoice can now be "
"created by clicking :guilabel:`Create Invoice` in the top-left corner. On "
"the :guilabel:`Create invoice(s)` pop-up window that appears, "
"select :guilabel:`Down payment (percentage)`, and type `100` in "
"the :guilabel:`Down Payment` field."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengonfigurasi uang muka 100%, navigasi ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi "
"Penjualan --> Baru` dan tambahkan :guilabel:`Pelanggan` ke penawaran. "
"Selanjutnya, klik :guilabel:`Tambahkan produk` di tab :guilabel:`Baris "
"Pesanan`, dan pilih produk `Solar Panel Installation`. Setelah mengklik "
"tombol :guilabel:`Konfirmasi`, penawaran berubah menjadi sales order. Pada "
"titik tersebut, faktur sekarang dapat dibuat dengan mengklik :guilabel:`Buat "
"Faktur` di sudut kiri atas. Pada jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Buat faktur` yang "
"muncul, pilih :guilabel:`Uang muka (persentase)`, dan ketik `100` di kolom "
":guilabel:`Uang Muka`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Down payment (percentage) option selected with 100% set as the Down "
"Payment."
msgstr ""
"Opsi Uang muka (persentase) dipilih dengan 100% ditetapkan sebagai Uang Muka."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:194
msgid ""
"Next, click :guilabel:`Create Draft Invoice` to create an invoice draft. "
"This will also bring the draft invoice into view, which includes "
"the :guilabel:`Down payment` under the :guilabel:`Down Payments` section of "
"the :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` tab. The invoice can now be confirmed and "
"posted by clicking :guilabel:`Confirm`. Confirming the invoice changes the "
"status from :guilabel:`Draft` to :guilabel:`Posted`. It also reveals a new "
"series of buttons at the top of the page."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, klik :guilabel:`Buat Draf Faktur` untuk membuat draf faktur. "
"Ini juga akan menampilkan draf faktur, yang mencakup :guilabel:`Uang muka` "
"di bawah bagian :guilabel:`Uang Muka` pada tab :guilabel:`Baris Faktur`. "
"Faktur sekarang dapat dikonfirmasi dan diposting dengan mengklik "
":guilabel:`Konfirmasi`. Mengonfirmasi faktur mengubah status dari "
":guilabel:`Draf` menjadi :guilabel:`Diposting`. Ini juga memunculkan "
"serangkaian tombol baru di bagian atas halaman."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:200
msgid ""
"The payment can be registered by clicking the :guilabel:`Pay` button. This "
"brings up the :guilabel:`Pay` pop-up form, which is auto-populated with the "
"necessary information. When ready, click the :guilabel:`Create Payment` "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Pembayaran dapat didaftarkan dengan mengklik tombol :guilabel:`Bayar`. Ini "
"memunculkan formulir pop-up :guilabel:`Bayar`, yang secara otomatis terisi "
"dengan informasi yang diperlukan. Ketika siap, klik tombol :guilabel:`Buat "
"Pembayaran`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:204
msgid ""
"After clicking :guilabel:`Create Payment`, Odoo reveals the customer "
"invoice, now with a green :guilabel:`In Payment` or :guilabel:`Paid` banner "
"in the upper-right corner, depending on how the database has configured and "
"if manual confirmation of payments is required. The process is now complete, "
"and the 100% down payment has been successfully applied."
msgstr ""
"Setelah mengklik :guilabel:`Buat Pembayaran`, Odoo menampilkan faktur "
"pelanggan, sekarang dengan banner hijau :guilabel:`Dalam Pembayaran` atau "
":guilabel:`Dibayar` di sudut kanan atas, tergantung pada bagaimana database "
"telah dikonfigurasi dan apakah konfirmasi manual pembayaran diperlukan. "
"Prosesnya sekarang selesai, dan uang muka 100% telah berhasil diterapkan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:212
msgid "Income account modification on down payments"
msgstr "Modifikasi akun pendapatan pada uang muka"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:215
msgid ""
"To change or adjust the income account attached to down payments, the "
"**Accounting** app must be installed. With the **Accounting** app installed, "
"the :guilabel:`Accounting` column becomes available on the draft invoice."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengubah atau menyesuaikan akun pendapatan yang terkait dengan uang "
"muka, aplikasi **Akuntansi** harus diinstal. Dengan aplikasi **Akuntansi** "
"terinstal, kolom :guilabel:`Akuntansi` menjadi tersedia pada draf faktur."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:219
msgid ""
"Navigate to the invoice to be modified by going to :menuselection:`Sales app "
"--> Orders --> Orders`. Open an order, then click the :guilabel:`Invoices` "
"smart button. Open an invoice, click the drop-down arrow on the entry in "
"the :guilabel:`Account` column and click :guilabel:`Search more...` to bring "
"up the :guilabel:`Search: Account` form. In this form, a different account "
"can be chosen from the list of pre-existing accounts. A new account can also "
"be created by clicking the :guilabel:`New` button."
msgstr ""
"Navigasi ke faktur yang akan dimodifikasi dengan pergi ke "
":menuselection:`Aplikasi Penjualan --> Pesanan --> Pesanan`. Buka pesanan, "
"kemudian klik tombol pintar :guilabel:`Faktur`. Buka faktur, klik panah drop-"
"down pada entri di kolom :guilabel:`Akun` dan klik :guilabel:`Cari lebih "
"banyak...` untuk memunculkan formulir :guilabel:`Cari: Akun`. Dalam formulir "
"ini, akun yang berbeda dapat dipilih dari daftar akun yang sudah ada. Akun "
"baru juga dapat dibuat dengan mengklik tombol :guilabel:`Baru`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Search:Account form with existing accounts displayed and a button to "
"create a new\n"
"account."
msgstr ""
"Formulir Cari:Akun dengan akun yang ada ditampilkan dan tombol untuk membuat "
"akun baru."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:231
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:114
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:71
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:166
msgid ":doc:`invoicing_policy`"
msgstr ":doc:`invoicing_policy`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:3
msgid "Invoicing policies"
msgstr "Kebijakan penagihan"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:5
msgid ""
"Depending on business needs, it may be advantageous to choose whether to "
"invoice customers based on the goods and services that they order or when "
"those goods and services are delivered to them. To allow businesses maximum "
"flexibility to best meet their needs, Odoo offers two invoicing policies "
"that can be enabled in the **Sales** app: :ref:`Invoice what is ordered "
"<invoice-on-order>` and :ref:`Invoice what is delivered <invoice-on-"
"delivery>`."
msgstr ""
"Tergantung pada kebutuhan bisnis, mungkin menguntungkan untuk memilih apakah "
"akan menagih pelanggan berdasarkan barang dan layanan yang mereka pesan atau "
"ketika barang dan layanan tersebut dikirimkan kepada mereka. Untuk "
"memberikan fleksibilitas maksimal bagi bisnis agar dapat memenuhi kebutuhan "
"mereka dengan sebaik-baiknya, Odoo menawarkan dua kebijakan penagihan yang "
"dapat diaktifkan di aplikasi **Penjualan**: :ref:`Invoice what is ordered "
"<invoice-on-order>` dan :ref:`Invoice what is delivered <invoice-on-delivery>"
"`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:11
msgid ""
"The *Invoice what is ordered* rule is used as the default mode in Odoo "
"**Sales**, which means customers are invoiced once the sales order is "
"confirmed."
msgstr ""
"Aturan *Tagih apa yang dipesan* digunakan sebagai mode default di Odoo "
"**Penjualan**, yang berarti pelanggan difaktur setelah sales order "
"dikonfirmasi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:13
msgid ""
"The *Invoice what is delivered* rule invoices customers once the delivery is "
"done. This rule is often used for businesses that sell materials, liquids, "
"or food in large quantities. In these cases, the ordered quantity may differ "
"slightly from the delivered quantity, making it preferable to invoice the "
"quantity actually delivered. When the delivery order is validated, Odoo will "
"automatically decrease the on-hand quantity in the inventory."
msgstr ""
"Aturan *Tagih apa yang dikirim* memfaktur pelanggan setelah pengiriman "
"selesai. Aturan ini sering digunakan untuk bisnis yang menjual material, "
"cairan, atau makanan dalam jumlah besar. Dalam kasus ini, kuantitas yang "
"dipesan mungkin sedikit berbeda dari kuantitas yang dikirim, sehingga lebih "
"baik memfaktur kuantitas yang benar-benar dikirim. Ketika surat jalan "
"divalidasi, Odoo akan secara otomatis mengurangi kuantitas yang tersedia di "
"inventaris."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:19
msgid ""
"To configure an invoicing policy, go to :menuselection:`Sales app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, and under the :guilabel:`Invoicing` heading, "
"select an :guilabel:`Invoicing Policy` option: :guilabel:`Invoice what is "
"ordered` or :guilabel:`Invoice what is delivered`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengonfigurasi kebijakan penagihan, buka :menuselection:`Sales app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, dan di bawah judul :guilabel:`Invoicing`, pilih "
"opsi :guilabel:`Invoicing Policy`: :guilabel:`Invoice what is ordered` atau "
":guilabel:`Invoice what is delivered`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:23
msgid ""
"Activating an invoicing policy option automatically applies the chosen "
"option to all newly created products. Existing products **must** have their "
"invoicing policy manually updated on their product forms."
msgstr ""
"Mengaktifkan opsi kebijakan penagihan secara otomatis menerapkan opsi yang "
"dipilih ke semua produk yang baru dibuat. Produk yang sudah ada **harus** "
"diperbarui kebijakan penagihannya secara manual pada formulir produk mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:None
msgid "Choosing an invoicing policy in the Sales app."
msgstr "Memilih kebijakan penagihan di aplikasi Penjualan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:31
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Invoice what is delivered` option is chosen, it is **not** "
"possible to activate the :guilabel:`Automatic Invoice` feature, which "
"automatically generates invoices when an online payment is confirmed. "
"Regular draft invoices can only be created once the delivery order has been "
"processed and validated."
msgstr ""
"Jika opsi :guilabel:`Invoice what is delivered` dipilih, **tidak** "
"memungkinkan untuk mengaktifkan fitur :guilabel:`Automatic Invoice`, yang "
"secara otomatis menghasilkan invoice ketika pembayaran online dikonfirmasi. "
"Invoice draf reguler hanya dapat dibuat setelah surat jalan diproses dan "
"divalidasi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:37
msgid "Changing the invoicing policy for existing products"
msgstr "Mengubah kebijakan penagihan untuk produk yang sudah ada"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:39
msgid ""
"After the invoicing policy has been configured in *Settings*, navigate to a "
"product's form through :menuselection:`Sales app --> Products --> Products` "
"and choosing a product. Locate the :guilabel:`Invoicing Policy` option "
"located under the :guilabel:`General Information` tab. Use the drop-down "
"menu to change the policy."
msgstr ""
"Setelah kebijakan penagihan dikonfigurasi di *Settings*, navigasi ke "
"formulir produk melalui :menuselection:`Sales app --> Products --> Products` "
"dan pilih produk. Temukan opsi :guilabel:`Invoicing Policy` yang terletak di "
"bawah tab :guilabel:`General Information`. Gunakan menu drop-down untuk "
"mengubah kebijakan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:None
msgid "How to change invoicing policy on a product form in the **Sales** app."
msgstr ""
"Cara mengubah kebijakan penagihan pada formulir produk di aplikasi "
"**Penjualan**."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:50
msgid "Invoicing what is ordered"
msgstr "Menagih apa yang dipesan"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:52
msgid ""
"The *Invoice what is ordered* option is used as the default mode in the "
"**Sales** app, which means customers are invoiced once a quotation has been "
"sent to the customer and confirmed. The creation of a quotation in turn "
"leads to the creation and confirmation of a sales order. An invoice can then "
"be created as soon as the sales order is confirmed."
msgstr ""
"Opsi *Invoice what is ordered* digunakan sebagai mode default di aplikasi "
"**Penjualan**, yang berarti pelanggan ditagih setelah penawaran dikirim ke "
"pelanggan dan dikonfirmasi. Pembuatan penawaran pada gilirannya mengarah "
"pada pembuatan dan konfirmasi Sales Order. Invoice kemudian dapat dibuat "
"segera setelah Sales Order dikonfirmasi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:57
msgid "This invoicing policy has no impact on the basic Odoo sales flow."
msgstr "Kebijakan penagihan ini tidak berdampak pada alur penjualan dasar Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:60
msgid "Invoice ordered quantity workflow"
msgstr "Alur kerja faktur berdasarkan kuantitas pesanan"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:62
msgid ""
"Confirm that the product's invoicing policy is set to :guilabel:`Ordered "
"quantities` in the product form. :ref:`Create a quotation and sales order "
"<sales/create-quotation>` as normal. After the sales order has been "
"confirmed, create an invoice by clicking the :guilabel:`Create Invoice` "
"button on the sales order form. Choose the type of invoice to be sent, "
"click :guilabel:`Create Draft Invoice`, confirm the invoice when ready, and "
"proceed with the payment flow as normal."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan bahwa kebijakan penagihan produk diatur ke :guilabel:`Ordered "
"quantities` di formulir produk. :ref:`Buat penawaran harga dan sales order "
"<sales/create-quotation>` seperti biasa. Setelah sales order dikonfirmasi, "
"buat faktur dengan mengklik tombol :guilabel:`Create Invoice` di formulir "
"sales order. Pilih jenis faktur yang akan dikirim, klik :guilabel:`Create "
"Draft Invoice`, konfirmasi faktur saat sudah siap, dan lanjutkan dengan alur "
"pembayaran seperti biasa."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:69
msgid ""
"A independent artisan with a small business sells handmade jewelery "
"nationwide online. Because they have direct control over their inventory "
"levels and ship with 3rd party carriers, they invoice their customers after "
"a sales order has been confirmed."
msgstr ""
"Seorang pengrajin independen dengan bisnis kecil menjual perhiasan buatan "
"tangan secara online ke seluruh negeri. Karena mereka memiliki kontrol "
"langsung atas tingkat inventaris mereka dan mengirim dengan kurir pihak "
"ketiga, mereka menagih pelanggan mereka setelah sales order dikonfirmasi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:73
msgid ""
"The artisan receives an order for a necklace. They send their customer a "
"quotation, confirm it, and create a sales order. After the sales order has "
"been confirmed, an invoice can be created and sent to the customer for "
"payment without any additional steps be taken. The invoice gets paid, the "
"necklace is shipped and delivered, and the transaction is complete."
msgstr ""
"Pengrajin tersebut menerima pesanan untuk sebuah kalung. Mereka mengirim "
"penawaran harga kepada pelanggan, mengonfirmasinya, dan membuat sales order. "
"Setelah sales order dikonfirmasi, faktur dapat dibuat dan dikirim ke "
"pelanggan untuk pembayaran tanpa langkah tambahan apa pun. Faktur dibayar, "
"kalung dikirim dan diterima, dan transaksi selesai."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:81
msgid "Invoicing what is delivered"
msgstr "Menagih apa yang dikirim"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:83
msgid ""
"The *Invoice what is delivered* option invoices customers as different "
"amounts of the ordered goods are delivered. This option is often used for "
"businesses that sell large quantities of physical goods in each sales order, "
"but may not always be able to completely fulfill a given order all at once. "
"In these cases, the ordered quantity may differ slightly from the delivered "
"quantity based on product availability. Once a quotation is confirmed, and "
"the status changes from :guilabel:`Quotation sent` to :guilabel:`Sales "
"order`, Odoo automatically adds both the delivered and invoiced quantities "
"to the invoice and sales order. Both partial and complete deliveries are "
"tracked. :ref:`Backorders <inventory/shipping/backorders>` can be created "
"for partial orders that will be completed at a later time."
msgstr ""
"Opsi *Invoice what is delivered* menagih pelanggan sesuai dengan jumlah "
"barang yang dikirim secara bertahap. Opsi ini sering digunakan untuk bisnis "
"yang menjual barang fisik dalam jumlah besar di setiap sales order, tetapi "
"tidak selalu dapat memenuhi pesanan sepenuhnya sekaligus. Dalam kasus ini, "
"kuantitas pesanan mungkin sedikit berbeda dari kuantitas yang dikirim "
"berdasarkan ketersediaan produk. Setelah penawaran harga dikonfirmasi, dan "
"statusnya berubah dari :guilabel:`Quotation sent` menjadi :guilabel:`Sales "
"order`, Odoo secara otomatis menambahkan kuantitas yang dikirim dan ditagih "
"ke faktur dan sales order. Baik pengiriman parsial maupun lengkap dilacak. "
":ref:`Backorders <inventory/shipping/backorders>` dapat dibuat untuk pesanan "
"parsial yang akan diselesaikan di lain waktu."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:93
msgid ""
"This invoicing policy has a minor impact on the sales flow because the "
"delivered quantity of a product needs to be manually entered on the sales "
"order."
msgstr ""
"Kebijakan penagihan ini memiliki dampak kecil pada alur penjualan karena "
"kuantitas produk yang dikirim perlu dimasukkan secara manual di sales order."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:None
msgid "How to see delivered and invoiced quantities on Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Cara melihat kuantitas yang dikirim dan ditagih di Odoo Sales."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:100
msgid "Invoice delivered quantity workflow"
msgstr "Alur kerja faktur berdasarkan kuantitas yang dikirim"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:102
msgid ""
"Confirm that the product's invoicing policy is set to :guilabel:`Delivered "
"quantities` in the product form. :ref:`Create a quotation and sales order "
"<sales/create-quotation>` as normal. After the sales order has been "
"confirmed, the product must be delivered before an invoice can be created."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan bahwa kebijakan penagihan produk diatur ke :guilabel:`Delivered "
"quantities` di formulir produk. :ref:`Buat penawaran harga dan sales order "
"<sales/create-quotation>` seperti biasa. Setelah sales order dikonfirmasi, "
"produk harus dikirim sebelum faktur dapat dibuat."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:106
msgid ""
"Once the product has been shipped and delivery has been confirmed, click "
"the :guilabel:`Delivery` smart button on the sales order screen and "
"click :guilabel:`Validate` to validate the delivery order. Once at least a "
"partial delivery has been confirmed, return to the sales order form. "
"The :guilabel:`Create Invoice` button is now purple to indicate that an "
"invoice can be created and confirmed, and that it is possible to proceed "
"with the payment flow as normal."
msgstr ""
"Setelah produk dikirim dan pengiriman dikonfirmasi, klik tombol pintar "
":guilabel:`Delivery` di layar sales order dan klik :guilabel:`Validate` "
"untuk memvalidasi surat jalan. Setelah setidaknya pengiriman parsial "
"dikonfirmasi, kembali ke formulir sales order. Tombol :guilabel:`Create "
"Invoice` sekarang berwarna ungu untuk menunjukkan bahwa faktur dapat dibuat "
"dan dikonfirmasi, dan bahwa dimungkinkan untuk melanjutkan dengan alur "
"pembayaran seperti biasa."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:113
msgid ""
"If a user attempts to create an invoice without validating the delivered "
"quantity, the system returns an error message alerting them to the issue."
msgstr ""
"Jika user mencoba membuat faktur tanpa memvalidasi kuantitas yang dikirim, "
"sistem akan mengembalikan pesan kesalahan yang memperingatkan mereka tentang "
"masalah tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:0
msgid ""
"If Delivered Quantities invoicing policy is chosen, ensure a quantity has "
"been\n"
"delivered."
msgstr ""
"Jika kebijakan penagihan Kuantitas Terkirim dipilih, pastikan kuantitas "
"telah dikirim."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:121
msgid ""
"A produce distributor using the invoice what is delivered option sells 50 "
"heads of lettuce to a local restaurant. At the time the delivery is made, "
"only 40 heads are available. The distributor delivers the available heads of "
"lettuce and creates an invoice for what was delivered. Later, when more "
"supply comes in, the distributor delivers the remaning 10 heads of lettuce "
"and creates a second invoice to complete the order."
msgstr ""
"Seorang distributor produk segar yang menggunakan opsi invoice what is "
"delivered menjual 50 kuntum selada kepada sebuah restoran lokal. Pada saat "
"pengiriman dilakukan, hanya 40 kuntum yang tersedia. Distributor mengirim "
"kuntum selada yang tersedia dan membuat faktur untuk apa yang dikirim. "
"Kemudian, ketika pasokan lebih banyak datang, distributor mengirim 10 kuntum "
"selada yang tersisa dan membuat faktur kedua untuk menyelesaikan pesanan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:128
msgid ":doc:`../sales_quotations/create_quotations`"
msgstr ":doc:`../sales_quotations/create_quotations`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:129
msgid ":doc:`down_payment`"
msgstr ":doc:`down_payment`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:131
msgid ""
":doc:`../../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/multipack`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`../../../inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/multipack`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:3
msgid "Invoice project milestones"
msgstr "Faktur milestone project"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:8
msgid ""
"Milestone-based invoicing is designed for companies that deliver work in "
"clearly defined phases. Instead of invoicing an entire service upfront or at "
"the very end, businesses can bill customers progressively as each stage of "
"work is completed. This approach provides customers clearer visibility into "
"progress and value delivered over time."
msgstr ""
"Penagihan berbasis milestone dirancang untuk perusahaan yang menyelesaikan "
"pekerjaan dalam fase yang terdefinisi dengan jelas. Alih-alih menagih "
"seluruh layanan di muka atau di akhir, bisnis dapat menagih pelanggan secara "
"progresif saat setiap tahap pekerjaan selesai. Pendekatan ini memberikan "
"pelanggan visibilitas yang lebih jelas terhadap kemajuan dan nilai yang "
"diberikan dari waktu ke waktu."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:13
msgid ""
"In Odoo, milestone invoicing is configured at the product level in the "
"**Sales** app, with milestone progress and completion managed in the "
"**Projects** app. When a milestone is marked as reached, the delivered "
"quantity on the sales order (SO) is updated and can be invoiced."
msgstr ""
"Di Odoo, penagihan milestone dikonfigurasi di tingkat produk dalam aplikasi "
"**Penjualan**, dengan kemajuan dan penyelesaian milestone dikelola dalam "
"aplikasi **Project**. Ketika milestone ditandai sebagai tercapai, kuantitas "
"terkirim pada sales order (SO) diperbarui dan dapat ditagih."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:18
msgid "How milestone invoicing works"
msgstr "Cara kerja penagihan milestone"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:20
msgid ""
"Milestone invoicing follows a clear workflow involving multiple applications "
"in Odoo:"
msgstr ""
"Penagihan milestone mengikuti alur kerja yang jelas yang melibatkan beberapa "
"aplikasi di Odoo:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:22
msgid ""
"A product is created in the **Sales** application, configured to be invoiced "
"based on milestones."
msgstr ""
"Produk dibuat dalam aplikasi **Penjualan**, dikonfigurasi untuk ditagih "
"berdasarkan milestone."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:23
msgid "A |SO| is created with the product."
msgstr "|SO| dibuat dengan produk tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:24
msgid ""
"A project in the **Projects** app is created with multiple milestones "
"included."
msgstr ""
"Proyek dalam aplikasi **Project** dibuat dengan beberapa milestone yang "
"disertakan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:25
msgid ""
"A milestone is reached, and marked complete, causing the *Delivered* "
"quantity on the |SO| line to update."
msgstr ""
"Milestone tercapai dan ditandai selesai, menyebabkan kuantitas *Delivered* "
"pada baris |SO| diperbarui."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:27
msgid ""
"An invoice is created for the completed milestone, which can be sent to the "
"customer."
msgstr ""
"Faktur dibuat untuk milestone yang telah selesai, yang dapat dikirim kepada "
"pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:30
msgid ""
"This document covers the **Sales** app configuration and invoicing flow for "
"invoicing based on project milestones. For more information on creating, "
"managing, and marking milestones as complete, and how to link them to tasks, "
"see :doc:`Project milestones <../../../services/project/project_management/"
"project_milestones>`."
msgstr ""
"Dokumen ini membahas konfigurasi aplikasi **Penjualan** dan alur penagihan "
"untuk penagihan berdasarkan milestone proyek. Untuk informasi lebih lanjut "
"tentang membuat, mengelola, dan menandai milestone sebagai selesai, serta "
"cara menautkannya ke tugas, lihat :doc:`Milestone proyek <../../../services/"
"project/project_management/project_milestones>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:36
msgid "Create milestone products"
msgstr "Buat produk milestone"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:38
msgid ""
"To begin, a service product must be configured specifically for milestone-"
"based invoicing. Navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Products --> "
"Products` and click :guilabel:`New`. Enter the necessary information, "
"including the product title and :guilabel:`Sales Price`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memulai, produk layanan harus dikonfigurasi khusus untuk penagihan "
"berbasis milestone. Navigasi ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi Penjualan --> "
"Produk --> Produk` dan klik :guilabel:`Baru`. Masukkan informasi yang "
"diperlukan, termasuk judul produk dan :guilabel:`Harga Jual`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:42
msgid ""
"For the :guilabel:`Product Type`, select :guilabel:`Service`. Doing so "
"reveals the :guilabel:`Create on Order` field. Select "
"either :guilabel:`Project`, :guilabel:`Project and Task`, "
"or :guilabel:`Task`, depending on how the product is to be tracked in the "
"**Project** app."
msgstr ""
"Untuk :guilabel:`Tipe Produk`, pilih :guilabel:`Layanan`. Tindakan ini akan "
"memunculkan kolom :guilabel:`Buat saat Pesanan`. Pilih :guilabel:`Project`, "
":guilabel:`Project dan Tugas`, atau :guilabel:`Tugas`, tergantung pada "
"bagaimana produk akan dilacak dalam aplikasi **Project**."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:47
msgid ""
"A :guilabel:`Project Template` can also be selected for the product. "
"See :doc:`Project templates <../../../services/project/project_management/"
"project_templates>` for more information. Project templates can have "
"milestones defined, however, the *Quantity (%)* field must be manually "
"updated on each newly created project."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Templat Project` juga dapat dipilih untuk produk. Lihat "
":doc:`Templat proyek <../../../services/project/project_management/"
"project_templates>` untuk informasi lebih lanjut. Templat proyek dapat "
"memiliki milestone yang telah ditentukan, namun, kolom *Kuantitas (%)* harus "
"diperbarui secara manual pada setiap proyek yang baru dibuat."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:52
msgid ""
"For the :guilabel:`Invoicing Policy`, select :guilabel:`Based on "
"Milestones`. This option ensures that the product's delivered quantities "
"update automatically once a milestone is completed."
msgstr ""
"Untuk :guilabel:`Kebijakan Penagihan`, pilih :guilabel:`Berdasarkan "
"Milestone`. Opsi ini memastikan bahwa kuantitas yang dikirimkan dari produk "
"diperbarui secara otomatis setelah milestone selesai."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:56
msgid ""
"*Based on Milestones* is only available if there is at least one project "
"with *Milestones* enabled."
msgstr ""
"*Berdasarkan Milestone* hanya tersedia jika ada setidaknya satu proyek "
"dengan *Milestone* diaktifkan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:60
msgid "Defining milestones"
msgstr "Menentukan milestone"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:63
msgid ""
"This document focuses on the process of selling and invoicing a milestone "
"product in the **Sales** app. For more information on creating milestones in "
"the **Project** app, see :doc:`Project milestones <../../../services/project/"
"project_management/project_milestones>`."
msgstr ""
"Dokumen ini berfokus pada proses penjualan dan penagihan produk milestone "
"dalam aplikasi **Penjualan**. Untuk informasi lebih lanjut tentang membuat "
"milestone dalam aplikasi **Project**, lihat :doc:`Milestone proyek <../../../"
"services/project/project_management/project_milestones>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:67
msgid ""
"After the milestone product has been sold, a  *Milestones* smart button is "
"added to the |SO|. Click the smart button to view, edit, or create new "
"milestones."
msgstr ""
"Setelah produk milestone terjual, tombol pintar *Milestone* ditambahkan ke "
"|SO|. Klik tombol pintar untuk melihat, mengedit, atau membuat milestone "
"baru."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:70
msgid ""
"From here, the :guilabel:`Delivered %` can be altered. This amount equates "
"to the total cost of the |SO| that is billed when the milestone is reached."
msgstr ""
"Dari sini, :guilabel:`Terkirim %` dapat diubah. Jumlah ini setara dengan "
"total biaya |SO| yang ditagih saat milestone tercapai."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:74
msgid ""
"A company that provides pool installation services bills based on predefined "
"milestones as the work is completed. Each milestone equates to 25% of the "
"total services:"
msgstr ""
"Sebuah perusahaan yang menyediakan layanan instalasi kolam renang menagih "
"berdasarkan milestone yang telah ditentukan sebelumnya saat pekerjaan "
"selesai. Setiap milestone setara dengan 25% dari total layanan:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:77
msgid "Site Preparation & Excavation"
msgstr "Persiapan Lokasi & Penggalian"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:78
msgid "Structural Installation"
msgstr "Instalasi Struktural"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:79
msgid "Plumbing & Equipment Installation"
msgstr "Instalasi Pipa & Peralatan"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:80
msgid "Finishing & Final Inspection"
msgstr "Penyelesaian & Inspeksi Akhir"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:None
msgid "The milestones for a sales order line."
msgstr "Milestone untuk baris sales order."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:85
msgid ""
"The team uses a project template, called *Pool installation*, with these "
"milestones defined. A new project is created whenever a |SO| with the *Pool "
"installation services* product is confirmed."
msgstr ""
"Tim menggunakan templat proyek, yang disebut *Instalasi kolam renang*, "
"dengan milestone yang telah ditentukan ini. Proyek baru dibuat setiap kali "
"|SO| dengan produk *Layanan instalasi kolam renang* dikonfirmasi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:90
msgid "Invoicing a completed milestone"
msgstr "Menagih milestone yang telah selesai"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:92
msgid ""
"Milestones can be tracked through the **Project** app (see :ref:`Using "
"milestones <project/using-milestones>`). Additionally, a milestone can be "
"marked complete by navigating to the |SO|, and clicking "
"the :guilabel:`Milestones` smart button. On the *Milestones* page, enable "
"the checkbox in the :guilabel:`Reached` column for the milestone."
msgstr ""
"Milestone dapat dilacak melalui aplikasi **Project** (lihat "
":ref:`Menggunakan milestone <project/using-milestones>`). Selain itu, "
"milestone dapat ditandai selesai dengan menavigasi ke |SO|, dan mengklik "
"tombol pintar :guilabel:`Milestone`. Pada halaman *Milestone*, aktifkan "
"kotak centang di kolom :guilabel:`Tercapai` untuk milestone tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:97
msgid ""
"Then, click :guilabel:`View Sales Order` or use the breadcrumbs to return to "
"the |SO|. The :guilabel:`Delivered` column will be updated to reflect the "
"*Delivered %* for the milestone reached."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`View Sales Order` atau gunakan breadcrumb untuk "
"kembali ke |SO|. Kolom :guilabel:`Delivered` akan diperbarui untuk "
"mencerminkan *Delivered %* untuk milestone yang tercapai."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:100
msgid ""
"These steps can be repeated as additional milestones are reached until the |"
"SO| has been fulfilled."
msgstr ""
"Langkah-langkah ini dapat diulangi saat milestone tambahan tercapai hingga "
"|SO| terpenuhi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:103
msgid ""
"Reaching a milestone does *not* automatically create an invoice. Instead, it "
"updates the |SO| to reflect the amount of the total that is ready for "
"invoicing."
msgstr ""
"Mencapai milestone *tidak* secara otomatis membuat invoice. Sebaliknya, ini "
"memperbarui |SO| untuk mencerminkan jumlah total yang siap untuk ditagih."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:106
msgid ""
"Once one or more milestones have been reached, navigate to the |SO|, and "
"confirm the :guilabel:`Delivered` column has updated correctly. Then, "
"click :guilabel:`Create Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah satu atau lebih milestone tercapai, navigasi ke |SO|, dan "
"konfirmasikan kolom :guilabel:`Delivered` telah diperbarui dengan benar. "
"Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Create Invoice`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:109
msgid ""
"Additional milestones can be invoiced as they are completed, until all "
"services are complete."
msgstr ""
"Milestone tambahan dapat ditagih saat selesai, hingga semua layanan selesai."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:112
msgid ":doc:`time_materials`"
msgstr ":doc:`time_materials`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:113
msgid ":doc:`proforma`"
msgstr ":doc:`proforma`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:3
msgid "Pro-forma invoices"
msgstr "Faktur pro-forma"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:5
msgid ""
"A *pro-forma invoice* is an abridged or estimated invoice sent in advance of "
"a delivery of goods. It notes the kind and quantity of goods, their value, "
"and other important information, such as weight and transportation charges."
msgstr ""
"*Faktur pro-forma* adalah faktur ringkas atau perkiraan yang dikirim sebelum "
"pengiriman barang. Ini mencatat jenis dan jumlah barang, nilainya, dan "
"informasi penting lainnya, seperti berat dan biaya transportasi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:9
msgid ""
"Pro-forma invoices are commonly used as preliminary invoices with a "
"quotation. They are also used during importation for customs purposes. They "
"differ from a normal invoice, in that they are *not* a demand (or request) "
"for payment."
msgstr ""
"Faktur pro-forma biasanya digunakan sebagai faktur awal dengan penawaran. "
"Faktur ini juga digunakan selama impor untuk keperluan bea cukai. Faktur ini "
"berbeda dari faktur normal, karena *bukan* merupakan permintaan (atau "
"tuntutan) untuk pembayaran."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:16
msgid ""
"In order to utilize pro-forma invoices, the *Pro-Forma Invoice* feature "
"**must** be activated."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menggunakan faktur pro-forma, fitur *Faktur Pro-Forma* **harus** "
"diaktifkan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:18
msgid ""
"To enable this feature, navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, and in the :guilabel:`Quotations \\& Orders` "
"section, click the checkbox next to :guilabel:`Pro-Forma Invoice`. Then, "
"click :guilabel:`Save` to save all changes."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengaktifkan fitur ini, buka :menuselection:`Aplikasi Penjualan --> "
"Konfigurasi --> Pengaturan`, dan di bagian :guilabel:`Penawaran \\& "
"Pesanan`, klik kotak centang di sebelah :guilabel:`Faktur Pro-Forma`. "
"Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Simpan` untuk menyimpan semua perubahan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:None
msgid "The Pro-Forma Invoice feature setting in the Odoo Sales application."
msgstr "Pengaturan fitur Pro-Forma Invoice di aplikasi Odoo Penjualan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:27
msgid "Send pro-forma invoice"
msgstr "Kirim faktur pro-forma"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:29
msgid ""
"With the :guilabel:`Pro-Forma Invoice` feature activated, the option to send "
"a pro-forma invoice is now available on any quotation or sales order, via "
"the :guilabel:`Send Pro-Forma Invoice` button."
msgstr ""
"Dengan fitur :guilabel:`Pro-Forma Invoice` diaktifkan, opsi untuk mengirim "
"faktur pro-forma kini tersedia di setiap penawaran atau sales order, melalui "
"tombol :guilabel:`Send Pro-Forma Invoice`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Send Pro-Forma Invoice button on a typical sales order in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Tombol Send Pro-Forma Invoice pada sales order umum di Odoo Penjualan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:37
msgid ""
"Pro-forma invoices can **not** be sent for a sales order or quotation if an "
"invoice for a down payment has already been sent, or for a recurring "
"subscription."
msgstr ""
"Faktur pro-forma **tidak dapat** dikirim untuk sales order atau penawaran "
"jika faktur untuk uang muka sudah dikirim, atau untuk langganan berulang."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:40
msgid ""
"In either case, the :guilabel:`Send Pro-Froma Invoice` button does **not** "
"appear."
msgstr ""
"Dalam kedua kasus tersebut, tombol :guilabel:`Send Pro-Froma Invoice` "
"**tidak** muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:42
msgid ""
"However, pro-forma invoices **can** be sent for services, event "
"registrations, courses, and/or new subscriptions. Pro-forma invoices are not "
"limited to physical, consumable, or storable goods."
msgstr ""
"Namun, faktur pro-forma **dapat** dikirim untuk layanan, registrasi acara, "
"kursus, dan/atau langganan baru. Faktur pro-forma tidak terbatas pada barang "
"fisik, habis pakai, atau dapat disimpan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:45
msgid ""
"When the :guilabel:`Send Pro-Forma Invoice` button is clicked, a pop-up "
"window appears, from which an email can be sent."
msgstr ""
"Ketika tombol :guilabel:`Send Pro-Forma Invoice` diklik, jendela pop-up "
"muncul, dari mana email dapat dikirim."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:48
msgid ""
"In the pop-up window, the :guilabel:`Recipients` field is auto-populated "
"with the customer from the sales order or quotation. The :guilabel:`Subject` "
"field and the body of the email can be modified, if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Di jendela pop-up, kolom :guilabel:`Recipients` secara otomatis terisi "
"dengan pelanggan dari sales order atau penawaran. Kolom :guilabel:`Subject` "
"dan isi email dapat dimodifikasi, jika diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:52
msgid ""
"The pro-forma invoice is automatically added as an attachment to the email."
msgstr "Faktur pro-forma secara otomatis ditambahkan sebagai lampiran ke email."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:54
msgid ""
"When ready, click :guilabel:`Send`, and Odoo instantly sends the email, with "
"the attached pro-forma invoice, to the customer."
msgstr ""
"Ketika siap, klik :guilabel:`Send`, dan Odoo langsung mengirim email, dengan "
"faktur pro-forma terlampir, ke pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:None
msgid ""
"The email pop-up window that appears with pro-forma invoice attached in Odoo "
"Sales."
msgstr ""
"Jendela pop-up email yang muncul dengan faktur pro-forma terlampir di Odoo "
"Penjualan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:62
msgid ""
"To preview what the pro-forma invoice looks like, click on the PDF at the "
"bottom of the email pop-up window *before* clicking :guilabel:`Send`. When "
"clicked, the pro-forma invoice is downloaded instantly. Open that PDF to "
"view (and review) the pro-forma invoice."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat pratinjau tampilan faktur pro-forma, klik PDF di bagian bawah "
"jendela pop-up email *sebelum* mengklik :guilabel:`Send`. Ketika diklik, "
"faktur pro-forma akan diunduh secara instan. Buka PDF tersebut untuk melihat "
"(dan meninjau) faktur pro-forma."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:0
msgid "Sample pro-forma invoice PDF from Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Contoh PDF faktur pro-forma dari Odoo Penjualan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:3
msgid "Invoicing based on time and materials"
msgstr "Penagihan berdasarkan waktu dan material"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:5
msgid ""
"Invoicing based on time and/or materials is typically used when accurately "
"estimating the size of a project isn't possible, or when the requirements of "
"a project may change."
msgstr ""
"Penagihan berdasarkan waktu dan/atau material biasanya digunakan ketika "
"estimasi ukuran proyek secara akurat tidak memungkinkan, atau ketika "
"persyaratan proyek dapat berubah."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:8
msgid ""
"This is different from a fixed-price contract, when a customer agrees to pay "
"a specified total for the fulfillment of the contract---no matter what needs "
"to be paid to the employees, sub-contractors, vendors, suppliers, and so on."
msgstr ""
"Ini berbeda dari kontrak harga tetap, ketika pelanggan setuju untuk membayar "
"total yang ditentukan untuk pemenuhan kontrak---terlepas dari apa yang perlu "
"dibayarkan kepada karyawan, sub-kontraktor, vendor, pemasok, dan sebagainya."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:12
msgid ""
"The Odoo *Sales* app can invoice for time and various other expenses (e.g. "
"transport, lodging), as well as purchases needed to fulfill an order."
msgstr ""
"Aplikasi *Penjualan* Odoo dapat menagih untuk waktu dan berbagai pengeluaran "
"lainnya (misalnya transportasi, akomodasi), serta pembelian yang diperlukan "
"untuk memenuhi pesanan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:16
msgid "App and settings configuration"
msgstr "Konfigurasi aplikasi dan pengaturan"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:18
msgid ""
"First, in order to accurately keep track of the progress of a project, the "
"Odoo *Project* and *Accounting* apps **must** be installed."
msgstr ""
"Pertama, untuk melacak kemajuan proyek secara akurat, aplikasi *Project* dan "
"*Akuntansi* Odoo **harus** diinstal."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:21
msgid ""
"To install the *Project* app, navigate to :menuselection:`Odoo main "
"dashboard --> Apps`. Then, on the :guilabel:`Apps` page, locate "
"the :guilabel:`Project` app block, and click :guilabel:`Activate`. The page "
"automatically refreshes and returns to the main Odoo dashboard, where the "
"*Project* app is now available to access."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menginstal aplikasi *Project*, buka :menuselection:`Dashboard utama "
"Odoo --> Apps`. Kemudian, di halaman :guilabel:`Apps`, temukan blok aplikasi "
":guilabel:`Project`, dan klik :guilabel:`Activate`. Halaman secara otomatis "
"dimuat ulang dan kembali ke dashboard utama Odoo, di mana aplikasi *Project* "
"kini tersedia untuk diakses."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:26
msgid "Repeat the same process to install the *Accounting* application."
msgstr "Ulangi proses yang sama untuk menginstal aplikasi *Akuntansi*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:28
msgid ""
"After installation, click the :guilabel:`Accounting` app icon from the main "
"Odoo dashboard, and navigate to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Settings`. "
"On the :guilabel:`Settings` page, scroll down to the :guilabel:`Analytics` "
"section, and ensure the box next to :guilabel:`Analytic Accounting` is "
"checked."
msgstr ""
"Setelah instalasi, klik ikon aplikasi :guilabel:`Akuntansi` dari dashboard "
"utama Odoo, dan buka :menuselection:`Configuration --> Settings`. Di halaman "
":guilabel:`Settings`, gulir ke bawah ke bagian :guilabel:`Analytics`, dan "
"pastikan kotak di samping :guilabel:`Analytic Accounting` dicentang."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"How it looks to activate the Analytic Accounting setting in Odoo Accounting "
"Setting page."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan untuk mengaktifkan pengaturan Analytic Accounting di halaman "
"Setting Akuntansi Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:37
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:43
msgid "Then, click :guilabel:`Save` to save all changes."
msgstr "Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Save` untuk menyimpan semua perubahan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:39
msgid ""
"Then, navigate to :menuselection:`Odoo main dashboard --> Project app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`. On the :guilabel:`Settings` page, in "
"the :guilabel:`Time Management` section, ensure the box beside "
"the :guilabel:`Timesheets` feature is checked."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, buka :menuselection:`Dashboard utama Odoo --> Aplikasi Project --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`. Di halaman :guilabel:`Settings`, pada bagian "
":guilabel:`Time Management`, pastikan kotak di samping fitur "
":guilabel:`Tabel Waktu` dicentang."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"What the Timesheets feature looks like on the Odoo Project settings page."
msgstr "Tampilan fitur Tabel Waktu di halaman pengaturan Project Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:52
msgid "Service product configuration"
msgstr "Konfigurasi produk layanan"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:54
msgid ""
"With the *Timesheets* feature activated in the *Project* app, it is now "
"possible to invoice for time spent on a project, but **only** when the "
"following product configurations have been made."
msgstr ""
"Dengan fitur *Tabel Waktu* diaktifkan di aplikasi *Project*, kini "
"dimungkinkan untuk menagih waktu yang dihabiskan pada sebuah proyek, tetapi "
"**hanya** ketika konfigurasi produk berikut telah dibuat."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:58
msgid ""
"Invoicing for time spent on a project is **only** possible with products "
"that have *Service* set as the *Product Type* on their product form."
msgstr ""
"Penagihan untuk waktu yang dihabiskan pada sebuah proyek **hanya** "
"dimungkinkan dengan produk yang memiliki *Service* sebagai *Product Type* "
"pada formulir produknya."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:61
msgid ""
"To configure a service product, first navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app "
"--> Products --> Products`. On the :guilabel:`Products` page, select the "
"desired service product to be configured, or click :guilabel:`New` to create "
"a new product."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengonfigurasi produk layanan, pertama buka :menuselection:`Aplikasi "
"Sales --> Products --> Products`. Di halaman :guilabel:`Products`, pilih "
"produk layanan yang ingin dikonfigurasi, atau klik :guilabel:`New` untuk "
"membuat produk baru."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:65
msgid ""
"From the product form, in the :guilabel:`General Information` tab, set "
"the :guilabel:`Product Type` to :guilabel:`Service`. Then, open the drop-"
"down menu in the :guilabel:`Invoicing Policy` field, and "
"select :guilabel:`Based on Timesheets`."
msgstr ""
"Dari formulir produk, pada tab :guilabel:`General Information`, atur "
":guilabel:`Product Type` menjadi :guilabel:`Service`. Kemudian, buka menu "
"drop-down pada bidang :guilabel:`Invoicing Policy`, dan pilih "
":guilabel:`Based on Timesheets`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:69
msgid ""
"Next, from the :guilabel:`Create on Order` drop-down menu, "
"select :guilabel:`Project \\& Task`. That setting indicates that, when a "
"sales order is created with this specific service product, a new project and "
"task is created in the *Project* app."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, dari menu drop-down :guilabel:`Create on Order`, pilih "
":guilabel:`Project \\& Task`. Pengaturan tersebut menunjukkan bahwa ketika "
"Sales Order dibuat dengan produk layanan tertentu ini, proyek dan tugas baru "
"dibuat di aplikasi *Project*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"The correct settings for Invoicing Policy and Create on Order fields for "
"service product."
msgstr ""
"Pengaturan yang benar untuk bidang Invoicing Policy dan Create on Order "
"untuk produk layanan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:78
msgid ""
"The option :guilabel:`Task` can be chosen instead from the :guilabel:`Create "
"on Order` drop-down menu. If :guilabel:`Task` is chosen, select an existing "
"project that the task will appear in from :guilabel:`Project` field, which "
"only appears if :guilabel:`Task` is chosen in the :guilabel:`Create on "
"Order` field."
msgstr ""
"Opsi :guilabel:`Task` dapat dipilih sebagai gantinya dari menu drop-down "
":guilabel:`Create on Order`. Jika :guilabel:`Task` dipilih, pilih proyek "
"yang sudah ada di mana tugas akan muncul dari bidang :guilabel:`Project`, "
"yang hanya muncul jika :guilabel:`Task` dipilih pada bidang "
":guilabel:`Create on Order`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:84
msgid "Add time spent to sales order"
msgstr "Tambahkan waktu yang dihabiskan ke Sales Order"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:86
msgid ""
"After properly configuring a service product with the correct *Invoicing "
"Policy* and *Create on Order* options, it is possible to add time spent to a "
"sales order."
msgstr ""
"Setelah mengonfigurasi produk layanan dengan benar dengan opsi *Invoicing "
"Policy* dan *Create on Order* yang tepat, dimungkinkan untuk menambahkan "
"waktu yang dihabiskan ke Sales Order."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:89
msgid ""
"To see that in action, navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app --> New` to "
"open a blank quotation form. Then, proceed to add a :guilabel:`Customer`, "
"and in the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab, click :guilabel:`Add a product`, and "
"select the properly :ref:`configured service product <sales/invoicing/"
"configured-service-product>` from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihatnya dalam praktik, buka :menuselection:`Aplikasi Sales --> New` "
"untuk membuka formulir penawaran kosong. Kemudian, lanjutkan untuk "
"menambahkan :guilabel:`Customer`, dan pada tab :guilabel:`Order Lines`, klik "
":guilabel:`Add a product`, dan pilih :ref:`produk layanan yang telah "
"dikonfigurasi <sales/invoicing/configured-service-product>` dari menu drop-"
"down."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:94
msgid "Next, click :guilabel:`Confirm` to confirm the order."
msgstr "Selanjutnya, klik :guilabel:`Confirm` untuk mengonfirmasi pesanan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:96
msgid ""
"After confirming the sales order, two smart buttons appear at the top of the "
"order form: :guilabel:`Projects` and :guilabel:`Tasks`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah mengonfirmasi Sales Order, dua tombol pintar muncul di bagian atas "
"formulir pesanan: :guilabel:`Projects` dan :guilabel:`Tasks`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"How the Projects and Tasks smart buttons look on a Sales Order in Odoo Sales."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan tombol pintar Projects dan Tasks pada Sales Order di Odoo Sales."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:103
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Projects` smart button is clicked, it reveals the specific "
"project related to this sales order. If the :guilabel:`Tasks` smart button "
"is clicked, it reveals the specific project task related to this sales "
"order. Both are also accessible in the *Project* app."
msgstr ""
"Jika tombol pintar :guilabel:`Projects` diklik, maka akan menampilkan "
"project spesifik yang terkait dengan sales order ini. Jika tombol pintar "
":guilabel:`Tasks` diklik, maka akan menampilkan tugas project spesifik yang "
"terkait dengan sales order ini. Keduanya juga dapat diakses di aplikasi "
"*Project*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:107
msgid ""
"In order to add time spent on a sales order, click the :guilabel:`Tasks` "
"smart button."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan waktu yang dihabiskan pada sales order, klik tombol pintar "
":guilabel:`Tasks`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:109
msgid ""
"On the task form, select the :guilabel:`Timesheets` tab. From "
"the :guilabel:`Timesheets` tab, employees can be assigned to work on the "
"project, and the time they spend working on the task can be added by the "
"employees or by the person who created the sales order."
msgstr ""
"Pada formulir tugas, pilih tab :guilabel:`Timesheets`. Dari tab "
":guilabel:`Timesheets`, karyawan dapat ditugaskan untuk mengerjakan project, "
"dan waktu yang mereka habiskan untuk mengerjakan tugas dapat ditambahkan "
"oleh karyawan atau oleh orang yang membuat sales order."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:113
msgid ""
"To add an employee, and the time spent working on the task, "
"click :guilabel:`Add a line` in the :guilabel:`Timesheets` tab. Then, select "
"the appropriate :guilabel:`Date` and :guilabel:`Employee`. There is also the "
"option to add a brief description of the work done during this time in "
"the :guilabel:`Description` column, but it's not required."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan karyawan dan waktu yang dihabiskan untuk mengerjakan "
"tugas, klik :guilabel:`Add a line` di tab :guilabel:`Timesheets`. Kemudian, "
"pilih :guilabel:`Date` dan :guilabel:`Employee` yang sesuai. Ada juga opsi "
"untuk menambahkan deskripsi singkat tentang pekerjaan yang dilakukan selama "
"waktu ini di kolom :guilabel:`Description`, tetapi ini tidak wajib."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:118
msgid ""
"Lastly, enter the amount of time worked on the task in the :guilabel:`Hours "
"Spent` column, and click away to complete that line in "
"the :guilabel:`Timesheets` tab."
msgstr ""
"Terakhir, masukkan jumlah waktu yang dikerjakan pada tugas di kolom "
":guilabel:`Hours Spent`, dan klik di luar untuk menyelesaikan baris tersebut "
"di tab :guilabel:`Timesheets`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:122
msgid ""
"The time entered in the :guilabel:`Hours Spent` column is immediately "
"reflected in the :guilabel:`Allocated Time` field (located near the top of "
"the task form) as a percentage, which reflects how much of the total "
"allocated work hours have been done so far."
msgstr ""
"Waktu yang dimasukkan di kolom :guilabel:`Hours Spent` langsung tercermin di "
"bidang :guilabel:`Allocated Time` (terletak di dekat bagian atas formulir "
"tugas) sebagai persentase, yang mencerminkan berapa banyak dari total jam "
"kerja yang dialokasikan telah diselesaikan sejauh ini."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:126
msgid ""
"That same information is found as numerical hours in the :guilabel:`Hours "
"Spent` and :guilabel:`Remaining Hours` fields, located at the bottom of "
"the :guilabel:`Timesheets` tab."
msgstr ""
"Informasi yang sama ditemukan sebagai jam numerik di bidang :guilabel:`Hours "
"Spent` dan :guilabel:`Remaining Hours`, yang terletak di bagian bawah tab "
":guilabel:`Timesheets`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:0
msgid ""
"How the Timesheets tab appears on a task form in Odoo Sales and Odoo Project."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan tab Timesheets pada formulir tugas di Odoo Sales dan Odoo Project."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:133
msgid ""
"Repeat this process for however many employees and hours have been worked on "
"the project."
msgstr ""
"Ulangi proses ini untuk berapa pun jumlah karyawan dan jam yang telah "
"dikerjakan pada project."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:136
msgid "Invoice time spent"
msgstr "Tagih waktu yang dihabiskan"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:138
msgid ""
"Once all the necessary employees and time spent have been added to the "
"project task, return to the sales order to invoice the customer for those "
"hours. To do that, either click the :guilabel:`Sales Order` smart button at "
"the top of the task form, or return to the sales order via the breadcrumb "
"links, located in the upper-left of the screen."
msgstr ""
"Setelah semua karyawan dan waktu yang dihabiskan telah ditambahkan ke tugas "
"project, kembali ke sales order untuk menagih pelanggan untuk jam-jam "
"tersebut. Untuk melakukannya, klik tombol pintar :guilabel:`Sales Order` di "
"bagian atas formulir tugas, atau kembali ke sales order melalui tautan "
"breadcrumb yang terletak di kiri atas layar."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:143
msgid ""
"Back on the sales order form, the time that was added to the task is "
"reflected in the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab (in the :guilabel:`Delivered` "
"column) and in the new :guilabel:`Recorded Hours` smart button at the top of "
"the sales order."
msgstr ""
"Kembali pada formulir sales order, waktu yang ditambahkan ke tugas tercermin "
"di tab :guilabel:`Order Lines` (di kolom :guilabel:`Delivered`) dan di "
"tombol pintar :guilabel:`Recorded Hours` yang baru di bagian atas sales "
"order."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:147
msgid ""
"To invoice the customer for time spent on the project, "
"click :guilabel:`Create Invoice`, and select :guilabel:`Regular invoice` "
"from the :guilabel:`Create invoices` pop-up window. Then, "
"click :guilabel:`Create Draft Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menagih pelanggan atas waktu yang dihabiskan pada project, klik "
":guilabel:`Create Invoice`, dan pilih :guilabel:`Regular invoice` dari "
"jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Create invoices`. Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Create "
"Draft Invoice`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:151
msgid ""
"Doing so reveals a :guilabel:`Customer Invoice Draft`, clearly showing all "
"the work that's been done in the :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` tab."
msgstr ""
"Melakukan hal ini akan menampilkan :guilabel:`Customer Invoice Draft`, yang "
"dengan jelas menunjukkan semua pekerjaan yang telah dilakukan di tab "
":guilabel:`Invoice Lines`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:155
msgid ""
"Pay attention to the :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` column in "
"the :guilabel:`Customer Invoice`, as that information is necessary to ensure "
"other time/material invoicing tasks are completed properly and accurately."
msgstr ""
"Perhatikan kolom :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` di :guilabel:`Customer "
"Invoice`, karena informasi tersebut diperlukan untuk memastikan tugas "
"penagihan waktu/material lainnya diselesaikan dengan benar dan akurat."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:0
msgid "Invoice draft showing time spent on sales order in Odoo Sales."
msgstr ""
"Draft invoice yang menampilkan waktu yang dihabiskan pada sales order di "
"Odoo Sales."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:163
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Confirm` to confirm the invoice and continue with the "
"invoicing process."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Confirm` untuk mengonfirmasi invoice dan melanjutkan proses "
"penagihan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:169
msgid "Expenses configuration"
msgstr "Konfigurasi pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:171
msgid ""
"In order to track and invoice expenses related to a sales order, the Odoo "
"*Expenses* app **must** be installed."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melacak dan menagih pengeluaran yang terkait dengan sales order, "
"aplikasi Odoo *Expenses* **harus** diinstal."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:174
msgid ""
"To install the *Expenses* app, navigate to :menuselection:`Odoo main "
"dashboard --> Apps`. Then, on the :guilabel:`Apps` page, locate "
"the :guilabel:`Expenses` app block, and click :guilabel:`Activate`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menginstal aplikasi *Pengeluaran*, navigasikan ke "
":menuselection:`Dashboard utama Odoo --> Apps`. Kemudian, pada halaman "
":guilabel:`Apps`, temukan blok aplikasi :guilabel:`Pengeluaran`, dan klik "
":guilabel:`Activate`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:178
msgid ""
"The page automatically refreshes and returns to the main Odoo dashboard, "
"where the :guilabel:`Expenses` app is now available to access."
msgstr ""
"Halaman secara otomatis menyegarkan dan kembali ke dashboard utama Odoo, di "
"mana aplikasi :guilabel:`Pengeluaran` sekarang tersedia untuk diakses."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:184
msgid "Add expenses to sales order"
msgstr "Tambahkan pengeluaran ke sales order"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:186
msgid ""
"To add an expense to a sales order, first navigate to "
"the :menuselection:`Expenses` app. Then, from the main *Expenses* dashboard, "
"click :guilabel:`New`, which reveals a blank expense form."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan pengeluaran ke sales order, pertama navigasikan ke "
"aplikasi :menuselection:`Pengeluaran`. Kemudian, dari dashboard "
"*Pengeluaran* utama, klik :guilabel:`New`, yang menampilkan formulir "
"pengeluaran kosong."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:189
msgid ""
"On the expense form, add a :guilabel:`Description` of the expense (e.g. "
"`Hotel Stay`, `Plane Ticket`). Next, in the :guilabel:`Category` field, "
"select the appropriate option from the drop-down menu "
"(e.g. :guilabel:`Meals`, :guilabel:`Miles`, :guilabel:`Travel \\& "
"Accommodation`)."
msgstr ""
"Pada formulir pengeluaran, tambahkan :guilabel:`Description` dari "
"pengeluaran (misalnya `Menginap di Hotel`, `Tiket Pesawat`). Selanjutnya, di "
"bidang :guilabel:`Category`, pilih opsi yang sesuai dari menu drop-down "
"(misalnya :guilabel:`Meals`, :guilabel:`Miles`, :guilabel:`Travel \\& "
"Accommodation`)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:194
msgid ""
"Expense categories can be added and modified by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> Configuration --> Expense Categories`."
msgstr ""
"Kategori pengeluaran dapat ditambahkan dan dimodifikasi dengan menavigasi ke "
":menuselection:`Aplikasi Pengeluaran --> Configuration --> Expense "
"Categories`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:197
msgid ""
"Then, enter the total amount of the expense in the :guilabel:`Total` field, "
"as well as any :guilabel:`Included Taxes` that may apply. Next, ensure that "
"the correct :guilabel:`Employee` is selected, and designate who paid for the "
"expense in the :guilabel:`Paid By` field: the :guilabel:`Employee (to "
"reimburse)` or the :guilabel:`Company`."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, masukkan jumlah total pengeluaran di bidang :guilabel:`Total`, "
"serta :guilabel:`Included Taxes` yang mungkin berlaku. Selanjutnya, pastikan "
":guilabel:`Employee` yang benar dipilih, dan tentukan siapa yang membayar "
"pengeluaran di bidang :guilabel:`Paid By`: :guilabel:`Employee (to reimburse)"
"` atau :guilabel:`Company`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:202
msgid ""
"Next, in the :guilabel:`Customer to Reinvoice` field, select the appropriate "
"sales order from the drop-down menu. Then, select that same sales order "
"information from the :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` field, as well."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, di bidang :guilabel:`Customer to Reinvoice`, pilih sales order "
"yang sesuai dari menu drop-down. Kemudian, pilih informasi sales order yang "
"sama dari bidang :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` juga."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:207
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` field will **only** have the "
"corresponding sales order as an option if the sales order contains a service "
"product that is billed based on *Timesheets*, *Milestones*, or *Delivered "
"Quantities*."
msgstr ""
"Bidang :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` akan **hanya** memiliki sales order "
"yang sesuai sebagai opsi jika sales order berisi produk layanan yang ditagih "
"berdasarkan *Timesheets*, *Milestones*, atau *Delivered Quantities*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"How to properly fill out an expense form that's attached to a sales order in "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Cara mengisi formulir pengeluaran dengan benar yang dilampirkan ke sales "
"order di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:215
msgid ""
"If there are any receipts that should be uploaded and attached to the "
"expense, click the :guilabel:`Attach Receipt` button, and upload the "
"necessary documents to the expense. This is **not** required, but it may "
"affect whether or not an expense is approved."
msgstr ""
"Jika ada tanda terima yang harus diunggah dan dilampirkan ke pengeluaran, "
"klik tombol :guilabel:`Attach Receipt`, dan unggah dokumen yang diperlukan "
"ke pengeluaran. Ini **tidak** wajib, tetapi dapat memengaruhi apakah "
"pengeluaran disetujui atau tidak."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:219
msgid ""
"When all the information has been entered, click :guilabel:`Create Report` "
"to create an expense report detailing all the expense information that was "
"just entered."
msgstr ""
"Setelah semua informasi dimasukkan, klik :guilabel:`Create Report` untuk "
"membuat laporan pengeluaran yang merinci semua informasi pengeluaran yang "
"baru saja dimasukkan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid "How an Expense Report Summary looks in Odoo Expenses."
msgstr "Tampilan Expense Report Summary di Odoo Pengeluaran."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:226
msgid ""
"Then, there's the option to :guilabel:`Submit to Manager` for approval. Once "
"approved, the :guilabel:`Report in Next Payslip` appears."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, ada opsi untuk :guilabel:`Submit to Manager` untuk persetujuan. "
"Setelah disetujui, :guilabel:`Report in Next Payslip` muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:229
msgid ""
"To showcase a complete flow in this example, select :guilabel:`Submit to "
"Manager`. Then, the manager would click :guilabel:`Approve` to approve this "
"expense, and click :guilabel:`Post Journal Entries` to post this expense to "
"the accounting journal."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menampilkan alur lengkap dalam contoh ini, pilih :guilabel:`Submit to "
"Manager`. Kemudian, manajer akan mengklik :guilabel:`Approve` untuk "
"menyetujui pengeluaran ini, dan klik :guilabel:`Post Journal Entries` untuk "
"memposting pengeluaran ini ke jurnal akuntansi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:234
msgid "Invoice expenses"
msgstr "Invoice pengeluaran"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:236
msgid ""
"To invoice a customer for an :ref:`expense on a sales order <sales/invoicing/"
"add-expenses-sales-order>`, navigate to the related sales order, either from "
"the :menuselection:`Sales` app or from the expense report in "
"the :menuselection:`Expenses` app. From the expense report, click "
"the :guilabel:`Sales Orders` smart button at the top of the page."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menagih pelanggan untuk :ref:`pengeluaran pada sales order <sales/"
"invoicing/add-expenses-sales-order>`, navigasikan ke sales order terkait, "
"baik dari aplikasi :menuselection:`Penjualan` atau dari laporan pengeluaran "
"di aplikasi :menuselection:`Pengeluaran`. Dari laporan pengeluaran, klik "
"tombol pintar :guilabel:`Sales Orders` di bagian atas halaman."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:241
msgid ""
"If the expense report was linked to the sales order, the newly-configured "
"expense now has its own line in the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab, and can be "
"invoiced to the customer."
msgstr ""
"Jika laporan pengeluaran ditautkan ke sales order, pengeluaran yang baru "
"dikonfigurasi sekarang memiliki barisnya sendiri di tab :guilabel:`Order "
"Lines`, dan dapat ditagih ke pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"An expense appearing on Order Lines tab of a Sales Order in Odoo Sales "
"application."
msgstr ""
"Pengeluaran yang muncul di tab Order Lines dari Sales Order di aplikasi Odoo "
"Penjualan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:248
msgid ""
"To invoice the customer for the expense on the sales order, "
"click :guilabel:`Create Invoice`, select :guilabel:`Regular Invoice` from "
"the :guilabel:`Create invoices` pop-up window, then click :guilabel:`Create "
"Draft Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menagih pelanggan untuk pengeluaran pada sales order, klik "
":guilabel:`Create Invoice`, pilih :guilabel:`Regular Invoice` dari jendela "
"pop-up :guilabel:`Create invoices`, kemudian klik :guilabel:`Create Draft "
"Invoice`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:252
msgid ""
"Doing so reveals a :guilabel:`Customer Invoice Draft` for the expense. Then, "
"the invoicing process can be completed as usual."
msgstr ""
"Dengan demikian akan muncul :guilabel:`Draf Faktur Pelanggan` untuk "
"pengeluaran tersebut. Kemudian, proses penagihan dapat diselesaikan seperti "
"biasa."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"Sample customer invoice for an expense generated from a sales order in Odoo "
"Sales."
msgstr ""
"Contoh faktur pelanggan untuk pengeluaran yang dihasilkan dari sales order "
"di Odoo Penjualan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:260
msgid "Purchase configuration"
msgstr "Konfigurasi pembelian"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:262
msgid ""
"In order to invoice a customer for purchases made on a sales order, the "
"*Purchase* application **must** be installed."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menagih pelanggan atas pembelian yang dilakukan pada sales order, "
"aplikasi *Pembelian* **harus** diinstal."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:265
msgid ""
"To install the *Purchase* application, navigate to :menuselection:`Odoo main "
"dashboard --> Apps`. Then, on the :guilabel:`Apps` page, locate "
"the :guilabel:`Purchase` app block, and click :guilabel:`Activate`. The page "
"automatically refreshes and returns to the main Odoo dashboard, where "
"the :guilabel:`Purchase` app is now available to access."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menginstal aplikasi *Pembelian*, navigasikan ke "
":menuselection:`Dashboard utama Odoo --> Aplikasi`. Kemudian, pada halaman "
":guilabel:`Aplikasi`, temukan blok aplikasi :guilabel:`Pembelian`, dan klik "
":guilabel:`Aktifkan`. Halaman akan otomatis dimuat ulang dan kembali ke "
"dashboard utama Odoo, di mana aplikasi :guilabel:`Pembelian` kini tersedia "
"untuk diakses."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:273
msgid "Add purchase to sales order"
msgstr "Tambahkan pembelian ke sales order"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:275
msgid ""
"To add a purchase to a sales order, a purchase order must first be created. "
"To create a purchase order, navigate to :menuselection:`Purchase app --> "
"New` to reveal a blank purchase order form."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan pembelian ke sales order, purchase order harus dibuat "
"terlebih dahulu. Untuk membuat purchase order, navigasikan ke "
":menuselection:`Aplikasi Pembelian --> Baru` untuk menampilkan formulir "
"purchase order kosong."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:278
msgid ""
"First, add a :guilabel:`Vendor` to the purchase order. Then, under "
"the :guilabel:`Products` tab, click the :guilabel:`extra column options` "
"drop-down menu, represented by two horizontal lines with dots on them, "
"located to the far-right of the column headers. From that drop-down menu, "
"select :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution`."
msgstr ""
"Pertama, tambahkan :guilabel:`Vendor` ke purchase order. Kemudian, di bawah "
"tab :guilabel:`Produk`, klik menu drop-down :guilabel:`opsi kolom tambahan`, "
"yang diwakili oleh dua garis horizontal dengan titik-titik di atasnya, yang "
"terletak di paling kanan header kolom. Dari menu drop-down tersebut, pilih "
":guilabel:`Distribusi Analitik`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"How to add analytic distribution column on purchase order form in Odoo "
"Purchase."
msgstr ""
"Cara menambahkan kolom distribusi analitik pada formulir purchase order di "
"Odoo Pembelian."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:287
msgid ""
"After adding the :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` column to the headers on "
"the :guilabel:`Products` tab of the purchase order form, proceed to add the "
"product(s) to the purchase order. To do that, click :guilabel:`Add a "
"product`, and select the desired product from the drop-down menu. Repeat for "
"all the products to add."
msgstr ""
"Setelah menambahkan kolom :guilabel:`Distribusi Analitik` ke header pada tab "
":guilabel:`Produk` formulir purchase order, lanjutkan untuk menambahkan "
"produk ke purchase order. Untuk melakukannya, klik :guilabel:`Tambahkan "
"produk`, dan pilih produk yang diinginkan dari menu drop-down. Ulangi untuk "
"semua produk yang ingin ditambahkan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:293
msgid ""
"In order for a purchase to be properly invoiced on a sales order, the "
"product on the purchase order **must** be marked as :guilabel:`Can be "
"Expensed`, have an :guilabel:`Invoicing Policy` set to :guilabel:`Delivered "
"quantities`, and have the :guilabel:`At cost` option selected in "
"the :guilabel:`Re-Invoice Expenses` field on its product form."
msgstr ""
"Agar pembelian dapat ditagihkan dengan benar pada sales order, produk pada "
"purchase order **harus** ditandai sebagai :guilabel:`Dapat Dibiayakan`, "
"memiliki :guilabel:`Kebijakan Penagihan` yang diatur ke :guilabel:`Jumlah "
"terkirim`, dan memiliki opsi :guilabel:`Sesuai biaya` yang dipilih di kolom "
":guilabel:`Penagihan Ulang Pengeluaran` pada formulir produknya."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:0
msgid ""
"Product settings for a purchase order to be invoiced on a sales order in "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Pengaturan produk agar purchase order dapat ditagihkan pada sales order di "
"Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:302
msgid ""
"Then, select the appropriate :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` associated "
"with the sales order to which this purchase order is related. To do that, "
"click the empty :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` field to reveal "
"an :guilabel:`Analytic` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, pilih :guilabel:`Distribusi Analitik` yang sesuai yang terkait "
"dengan sales order di mana purchase order ini terkait. Untuk melakukannya, "
"klik kolom :guilabel:`Distribusi Analitik` yang kosong untuk menampilkan "
"jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Analitik`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:306
msgid ""
"Then, from the :guilabel:`Departments` drop-down menu, select the analytic "
"distribution associated with the desired sales order to be invoiced for the "
"purchase."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, dari menu drop-down :guilabel:`Departemen`, pilih distribusi "
"analitik yang terkait dengan sales order yang diinginkan untuk ditagihkan "
"atas pembelian."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"How to select the Analytic Distribution department from a purchase order in "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Cara memilih departemen Distribusi Analitik dari purchase order di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:313
msgid ""
"Once all the information is entered in the :guilabel:`Products` tab of the "
"purchase order, confirm the order by clicking :guilabel:`Confirm Order`. "
"Then, click :guilabel:`Receive Products` when the products have been "
"received. This creates a receipt form."
msgstr ""
"Setelah semua informasi dimasukkan di tab :guilabel:`Produk` purchase order, "
"konfirmasi pesanan dengan mengklik :guilabel:`Konfirmasi Pesanan`. Kemudian, "
"klik :guilabel:`Terima Produk` ketika produk telah diterima. Ini akan "
"membuat formulir penerimaan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:318
msgid ""
"If any serial/lot numbers must be entered before validating the receipt of "
"products, then on the receipt form, click the :guilabel:`details` icon "
"represented by four horizontal lines located to the far-right of the product "
"line."
msgstr ""
"Jika nomor seri/lot harus dimasukkan sebelum memvalidasi penerimaan produk, "
"maka pada formulir penerimaan, klik ikon :guilabel:`detail` yang diwakili "
"oleh empat garis horizontal yang terletak di paling kanan baris produk."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:322
msgid ""
"This reveals a :guilabel:`Detailed Operations` tab, in which the "
"necessary :guilabel:`Lot/Serial Number(s)` and :guilabel:`Done` quantity can "
"be added. When ready, click :guilabel:`Confirm` to confirm the data."
msgstr ""
"Ini akan menampilkan tab :guilabel:`Operasi Terperinci`, di mana "
":guilabel:`Nomor Lot/Seri` yang diperlukan dan jumlah :guilabel:`Selesai` "
"dapat ditambahkan. Jika sudah siap, klik :guilabel:`Konfirmasi` untuk "
"mengonfirmasi data."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:326
msgid "Then, click :guilabel:`Validate` to validate the purchase order."
msgstr "Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Validasi` untuk memvalidasi purchase order."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:328
msgid ""
"Next, return to the purchase order, via the breadcrumb links at the top of "
"the page, and click :guilabel:`Create Bill` to create a vendor bill that can "
"be invoiced to the customer on the attached sales order."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, kembali ke purchase order melalui tautan breadcrumb di bagian "
"atas halaman, dan klik :guilabel:`Buat Tagihan` untuk membuat tagihan vendor "
"yang dapat ditagihkan kepada pelanggan pada sales order yang terlampir."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"Vendor bill draft for a purchase order to be invoiced to a customer in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Draf tagihan vendor untuk pesanan pembelian yang akan ditagihkan kepada "
"pelanggan di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:337
msgid ""
"Make sure to enter a :guilabel:`Bill Date` on the :guilabel:`Vendor Bill "
"Draft` before confirming. If a :guilabel:`Bill Date` is *not* entered, an "
"error window appears, requesting that information to be entered before "
"confirmation can occur."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan untuk memasukkan :guilabel:`Tanggal Tagihan` pada :guilabel:`Draf "
"Tagihan Vendor` sebelum mengonfirmasi. Jika :guilabel:`Tanggal Tagihan` "
"*tidak* dimasukkan, jendela error akan muncul, meminta informasi tersebut "
"dimasukkan sebelum konfirmasi dapat dilakukan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:341
msgid ""
"Then, click :guilabel:`Confirm` to confirm the vendor bill, which is then "
"automatically added to the sales order, where it can be invoiced directly to "
"the customer attached to it."
msgstr ""
"Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Konfirmasi` untuk mengonfirmasi tagihan vendor, "
"yang kemudian secara otomatis ditambahkan ke sales order, di mana dapat "
"ditagihkan langsung kepada pelanggan yang terlampir padanya."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:345
msgid "Invoice purchase"
msgstr "Tagihan pembelian"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:347
msgid ""
"To invoice a customer for a purchase on a sales order, first :ref:`add the "
"purchase to the sales order <sales/invoicing/add-purchase-to-sales-order>`, "
"then navigate to the desired sales order in the :menuselection:`Sales` app."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menagih pelanggan atas pembelian pada sales order, pertama "
":ref:`tambahkan pembelian ke sales order <sales/invoicing/add-purchase-to-"
"sales-order>`, kemudian navigasi ke sales order yang diinginkan di aplikasi "
":menuselection:`Penjualan`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:351
msgid ""
"On the sales order that was attached to the purchase order, the purchased "
"product now has its own product line under the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab, "
"and it is ready to be invoiced."
msgstr ""
"Pada sales order yang dilampirkan ke pesanan pembelian, produk yang dibeli "
"sekarang memiliki baris produknya sendiri di bawah tab :guilabel:`Baris "
"Pesanan`, dan siap untuk ditagihkan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"Purchase order product on sales order to be invoiced to customer via Odoo "
"Sales."
msgstr ""
"Produk pesanan pembelian pada sales order yang akan ditagihkan kepada "
"pelanggan melalui Odoo Sales."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:358
msgid ""
"To invoice the customer for the purchase, simply click :guilabel:`Create "
"Invoice`, select :guilabel:`Regular Invoice` from the :guilabel:`Create "
"invoices` pop-up window, then click :guilabel:`Create Draft Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menagih pelanggan atas pembelian, cukup klik :guilabel:`Buat Tagihan`, "
"pilih :guilabel:`Tagihan Reguler` dari jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Buat "
"tagihan`, kemudian klik :guilabel:`Buat Draf Tagihan`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:362
msgid ""
"Doing so reveals a :guilabel:`Customer Invoice Draft` with the newly-added "
"purchase order product in the :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` tab."
msgstr ""
"Dengan melakukan hal ini akan memunculkan :guilabel:`Draf Tagihan Pelanggan` "
"dengan produk pesanan pembelian yang baru ditambahkan di tab "
":guilabel:`Baris Tagihan`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"Customer invoice draft with purchase product attached to sales order in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Draf tagihan pelanggan dengan produk pembelian yang dilampirkan ke sales "
"order di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:369
msgid ""
"To complete the invoicing process, click :guilabel:`Confirm` to confirm the "
"invoice, and then click :guilabel:`Register Payment` in "
"the :guilabel:`Register Payment` pop-up form."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menyelesaikan proses penagihan, klik :guilabel:`Konfirmasi` untuk "
"mengonfirmasi tagihan, kemudian klik :guilabel:`Daftarkan Pembayaran` pada "
"formulir pop-up :guilabel:`Daftarkan Pembayaran`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector.rst:5
msgid "Lazada Connector"
msgstr "Konektor Lazada"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/features.rst:3
msgid "Lazada Connector features"
msgstr "Fitur Konektor Lazada"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/features.rst:5
msgid ""
"The **Lazada Connector** synchronizes orders, products, and inventory "
"between Lazada and Odoo, streamlining your operations across Southeast "
"Asia's marketplaces. It reduces manual data entry between systems and "
"enhances order management, enabling efficient tracking of Lazada sales "
"within Odoo."
msgstr ""
"**Konektor Lazada** menyinkronkan pesanan, produk, dan inventaris antara "
"Lazada dan Odoo, menyederhanakan operasi Anda di seluruh pasar Asia "
"Tenggara. Ini mengurangi entri data manual antar sistem dan meningkatkan "
"manajemen pesanan, memungkinkan pelacakan penjualan Lazada yang efisien di "
"dalam Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/lazada_connector/features.rst:13
msgid "The **Lazada Connector** is able to:"
msgstr "**Konektor Lazada** mampu untuk:"

