msgid ""
"Click on an eWallet to change the :guilabel:`Expiration "
"Date`, :guilabel:`Partner`, or :guilabel:`Balance`. The :guilabel:`Code` of "
"an eWallet *cannot* be changed, deleted, or duplicated."
msgstr ""
"Klik pada eWallet untuk mengubah :guilabel:`Tanggal Kedaluwarsa`, "
":guilabel:`Mitra`, atau :guilabel:`Saldo`. :guilabel:`Kode` eWallet *tidak "
"dapat* diubah, dihapus, atau diduplikasi."

